Ibipimo by'ubwiyongere bwihuse mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere k'ubukungu k'Uburayi n'Ubwongereza, kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020
Imiterere isa n'iy'ubwandu bw'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere ka Burayi n'u Bwongereza, igaragaza ko nubwo ibice bitandukanye mu gihugu, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyateye imbere mu buryo bwihuse mu bihugu byose.
Nk'uko byagenze mu Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 bigomba kongera ubushobozi bwo guhangana n'ubwiyongere bw'abanduye COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho n'abaganga n'abashinzwe kwitabwaho cyane.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, habonetse abantu benshi bafite uburwayi bw'ibicurane mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko icyateye iyi ndwara ari coronavirus nshya, ubu ikaba yitwa 2-SARS-CoV coronavirus y'ubuhumekero.
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara y'ubwandu buturuka kuri 2-SARS-CoV yamenyekanye nka COVID-19 coronavirus.
Kugeza ubu, ibihamya bigaragaza ko 80% by'abanduye COVID-19 barwara indwara yoroheje, ni ukuvuga indwara yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero itari iyo mu bihaha cyangwa irwaye mu bihaha, kandi abenshi muri bo barakira.
14% by'abanduye COVID-19 bakeneye kuvurirwa mu bitaro, naho 6% by'abanduye bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane.
Imibare y'abapfa bishwe na COVID-19 mu gihe cy'ibitotsi ni hafi 4%.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twasuzumye imibare y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cyo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere k'ubukungu k'Uburayi (EU/EEA) n'Ubwongereza, tuyigereranya n'ibyabaye mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Turagereranya kandi imibare y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bariho muri EU/EU Economic Area n'u Bwongereza n'iy'abarwayi bo mu Butaliyani kuva ku wa 31 Mutarama kugeza ku wa 15 Werurwe 2020.
Abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere ka Burayi k'Ubukungu n'u Bwongereza
Nyuma y'u Bushinwa, COVID-19 yagutse cyane mu karere, kandi icyorezo cya Coronavirus cyakwirakwiriye mu bindi bihugu byo ku isi.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, nk'uko Eurosurveillance 2020 ibivuga, Spiteri na bagenzi be batangaje ko ari bo bantu ba mbere bemejwe ko banduye COVID-19 mu Burayi nk'uko bitangazwa na OMS.
Mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere ka Burayi, abantu batatu ba mbere bemejwe ko banduye byemejwe ku itariki ya 24 Mutarama 2020 mu bantu bari bavuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, abantu banduye COVID-19 bari mu bihugu byose 30 bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi/Akarere ka Burayi n'Ubwongereza, aho kuva ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kugeza uyu wa mbere, hamaze kuboneka abantu 39,768 banduye, harimo 1,727 bapfuye, muri abo 17,750 banduye, naho 1,441 bapfuye bari mu Butaliyani gusa.
Gushyiraho umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 n'umubare w'abanduye
Ikigo cy'u Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (ECDC), kivuga ko imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu byose byo ku isi, itangwa gusa n'ibikoresho byemewe n'amategeko, urugero nk'ubushikiranganji bw'ubuzima bw'ibihugu, inzego z'ubuzima z'akarere na OMS, kandi ko ivugururwa buri munsi saa munani za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gupima icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi n'u Bwongereza, agereranywa n'u Butaliyani.
Nk'umuhuza mu iterambere ry'abanduye COVID-19, twagerageje imibare y'iminsi 14 y'abanduye COVID-19 mu buryo buciriritse, bityo dukurikiza icyiciro cya COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cyo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'Uburayi n'Ubwongereza kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Nanone kandi, twatanze imibare y'ibanze y'abanduye muri buri gihugu cyacu guhera saa munani z'igitondo ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, ugereranyije n'umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe.
COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza
Ibitekerezo by'ibanze by'iminsi 14 y'ubwiyongere bw'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, byakurikije cyane cyane ibyavuzwe mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa (Igishushanyo cya 1.
Mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi n'u Bwongereza muri rusange, ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwatangiye kwiyongera ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, bugera ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (Ibihamya).
Ibi byatewe ahanini n'ubwiyongere bwihuse bw'ubwandu mu Butaliyani, ariko ibindi bihugu byose bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi n'Ubwongereza byagaragaje ukwiyongera nk'uko mu bihugu byabo, umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 wiyongereye cyane.
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi n'u Bwongereza ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama-15 Werurwe 2020.
Ibi byerekana ko ku isaha ya saa munani z'igitondo ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, umubare w'abanduye mu bindi bihugu 15 bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi n'u Bwongereza wari ungana n'uw'abanduye mu Butaliyani mu byumweru bitatu cyangwa munsi y'aho.
Ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi bwacu bigaragaza ko imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi n'u Bwongereza iri kwiyongera cyane.
Ibipimo by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bigaragaza ko ubwiyongere bugenda buhinduka ku kigero kimwe mu bihugu byose.
Ibi kandi birashoboka nubwo ibihugu bitandukanye mu byiciro bitandukanye kandi bitajya bihuza mu buryo bwo gusubiza mu rwego rw'ubuzima rusange, ndetse no mu buryo bwo gusobanura icyorezo n'amabwiriza agenga icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu bice by'u Butaliyani byibasiwe n'icyorezo bavuze ko abagera kuri 10% by'abanduye COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane, kandi amakuru aturuka mu bitangazamakuru avuga ko ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi cyane muri utwo turere byamaze kugera ku rwego rwo hejuru.
Imibare y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 barembye mu bitaro no mu byumba by'indembe mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA ubu ni 6% na 1% by'abandura (amakuru ntabwo agaragara).
Icyakora, ibi bigomba gukusanywa mu buryo buteganyijwe kugira ngo amakuru y'ibanze agaragaza umubare w'abamaze kwandura n'umubare w'abapfuye ashobore gutangwa.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu Ugushyingo 2010 bugaragaza itandukaniro rinini mu mubare w'ibitanda by'ubuvuzi bwa intensive care n'iby'ubuvuzi mu bigo by'ubuvuzi mu Burayi, aho mu Budage hari ibitanda 29.2 ku bantu 100.000, naho muri Portugal hakaba ibitanda 4.2 ku bantu 100.000.
Ibi byerekana ko ibihugu bishobora kuba bifite umutungo muto cyangwa munini ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani (12.5 ibitanda by'ubuvuzi bw'ingufu n'ubwitonzi ku bantu 100,000 mu Ugushyingo 2020).
Ibipimo by'uburyo bwo kwitegura ku rwego rwo hejuru mu by'ubuvuzi, hamwe n'ibipimo by'ibihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi n'Ubwongereza ku byerekeranye n'ubwiyongere bw'abanduye COVID-19 bakeneye ko baruhuka, bifitanye isano n'ibyago byo kugabanya 90% by'ubwiyongere bw'abari mu byumba by'ubuvuzi bw'imbaraga, byashyizwe ahagaragara mu isesengura rya gatandatu ry'igikorwa cy'icungamutungo cy'ubuvuzi cya ECDC cyo kwihutisha icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Kubera ko abantu benshi cyane mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi n'u Bwongereza bafite uburwayi, kandi ibitaro n'ibyumba by'ubuvuzi bw'indembe bikorera abaturage bo mu karere runaka, ni byiza ko amakuru yerekeye uburwayi n'ibitanda by'ubuvuzi bw'indembe avugwa mu magambo y'ibyumba by'akarere ku rwego rwa 2 (2-NUTS).
Ibyabaye mu Butaliyani n'ibibera mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko COVID-19 ikwirakwira mu buryo bwihuse mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bakomeye bigomba kwitegura uko bizagenda mu gihe hazabaho ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 mu baturage, ndetse n'ubwiyongere bw'abanduye COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho mu buryo bwihariye, nk'uko bimeze mu bice by'u Butaliyani byugarijwe n'iki cyorezo.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe mu isuzuma ry'ibihe byihutirwa rya ECDC, uburyo bwuzuye, bwihuse kandi bwihuse ni ngombwa mu guteza imbere ikwirakwira rya 2-SARS-COV, hamwe no guhindura inzira kuva mu guhagarika kugeza mu kugabanya, kuko igihe gihagije kitari kuboneka ku bagena ibyemezo n'ibitaro kugirango basobanukirwe, bakore ubushakashatsi kandi bahindure uko babyifatamo niba bishoboka kandi mu gihe cyagenwe.
Igenzura ry'ibyago ryihutirwa kandi rigaragaza ingamba z'ubuzima rusange zo kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo.
Ubu hari uburyo buciriritse ibihugu bishobora kongera imbaraga mu kurwanya ikwirakwira rya koronavirusi 2-SARS-CoV no kugabanya igitutu ku rwego rw'ubuzima.
Ibi biramutse bitagenze neza, mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere, inzego z'ubuzima mu bindi bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'Uburayi zishobora gutangira guhangana n'abantu bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane.
Icyorezo cya 2019 ((19-COVID), cyatewe na Coronavirus ya 2 (2-SARS-CoV) -indwara y'ubuhumekero (SARS) kugeza ubu kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3,000 no kwandura abarenga 80,000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu ku isi, bikaba bishobora guteza abantu akaga.
Kimwe na SARS-CoV-2 ya mbere, yazanye abantu ibihumbi n'ibihumbi mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba yaratewe n'ikinyugunyugu kandi igatuma habaho ibimenyetso nk'ibyacyo.
COVID-19 ifite ubukana buciriritse n'ubwandu buciriritse, ariko ifite ubwandu bwinshi cyane kandi igera ku bagabo n'abagore bakuze kurusha abakiri bato.
Iyi ngingo igaragaza uko ubushakashatsi bwagiye bukomeza kwihuta, mu gihe habonetse imibare igenda yiyongera y'ibinyamakuru bivuga kuri iyi ndwara iherutse kuvuka.
Tuzasuzuma amahame y'ibanze y'ubushakashatsi ku ndwara, ku mpamvu, ku mikorobe, ku gupima, ku kuvura, ku kwitegura no kwirinda indwara.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bikeneye ibisubizo, twizeye ko iri suzuma rizadufasha gusobanukirwa no kwirinda iyi ndwara iteye ubwoba.
Umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi wo ku wa 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye urwibutso rudasanzwe ku Bashinwa kuko bagombaga kuguma mu rugo iminsi yose y'ikiruhuko mu gihe cy'ibyumweru byinshi nyuma y'icyorezo gishya cya virusi.
Iyi virusi isa cyane na coronavirus (CoV) yatumye habaho indwara y'ubuhumekero (SARS) mu 2003; bityo ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryayise SARS-CoV-2 coronavirus, naho indwara ihura na yo yitwa COVID-19.
Iki cyorezo cyatangiriye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, kigahita gikwirakwira mu gihugu hose ndetse no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 byo ku isi.
Ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi ya COVID-19 yari imaze kwemeza abantu 80,000, muri bo 40,000 bakira, naho abarenga 3,000 barapfa.
OMS iraburira ko COVID-19 ari "umwanzi rusange wa 1", kandi ko ikomeye cyane kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko PubMed ((https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/) ibivuga, mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri, hamaze gutangwa inyandiko zirenga 200 zivuga kuri COVID-19 zirimo ibijyanye n'ubumenyi bw'ubwandu, pathogenesis, causal biology, gusuzuma no kuvura indwara nyuma y'uko habonetse umuntu wa mbere wafashwe ku itariki ya 7 Mutarama 2020, kandi zigaragaza urutonde rwa virusi mu barwayi batandukanye.
Iyi mpuguke igerageza gusesengura uburyo ubushakashatsi muri iyi gazeti nshya buhagaze vuba mu gihe ikomeje gutera imbere.
Iyo bitangiye, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'izindi ndwara z'ubwandu bwa coronavirus na Middle East Respiratory Syndrome (MERS, 2012).
Nanone kandi, tuzasuzuma ibyo tuzi ku birebana no kwirinda no guhanura indwara, hamwe n'ibibazo by'ingenzi tugiye gusuzuma.
Coronavirus isanzwe ifatwa nk'ikintu cyandura abantu kitari mu gihe cyo kubyara, kandi mu by'ukuri itera 15% by'indwara zisanzwe ziterwa n'ibicurane.
Nyamara, muri iki kinyejana, twahuye n'ibicurane by'abantu by'ubwoko bubiri, SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, byateje icyorezo cya mbere mu Bushinwa mu 2003 no muri Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, kandi bidatinze byarakwirakwijwe mu bihugu byinshi byo ku isi, bigira ubwandu n'urupfu biteye ubwoba.
COVID-19 ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya coronavirus mu mateka y'abantu.
Nanone, nk'uko bigaragazwa ku ishusho ya 1.1, indwara z'ubuhumekero z'ibanze zitamenyekana, zatangajwe bwa mbere n'Ikigo cy'Igihugu cy'Ubuzima mu Bushinwa i Wuhan ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019.
Hashize icyumweru, hakurikiyeho gusohora urutonde rwa virusi ya corona.
Ku itariki ya 15 Mutarama 2020, nibwo habaye umuntu wa mbere wapfuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Kugeza icyo gihe, icyorezo cyari cyarakwirakwiriye mu mijyi, mu ntara no mu bihugu by'ibituranyi.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, habonetse amakuru y'ubwandu mu bakozi b'ubuzima, kandi byatangajwe ko iyi ndwara ishobora kwandura ku bantu.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, Wuhan yashyizwe mu kato kandi imodoka zose za leta zahagaritswe.
Ku ya 24 Ukuboza, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwagaragaje ko mu bantu 41 bemejwe ko banduye, 21 gusa ari bo bagaragaye ku isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja, bityo bikaba ari bwo bwa mbere habonetse ibimenyetso by'uko indwara yaturutse mu nyamaswa zitamenyekana.
Ku ya 30 Mutarama, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari icy'ubutabazi ku isi hose.
Kugeza ubu, iki cyorezo cyamaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa hose no mu bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi.
Kubera ko ibintu byihuta cyane, igihe n'uburemere bw'iyo gahunda yo kutagira aho bihuriye n'ibindi, bigomba gukomeza kuba urujijo.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi 8,866 bwerekanye ko 4,021 bafite COVID-19 bwerekanye ko icyorezo cyakomeje kwiyongera (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/Ul-Bi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
