Nyamara, icyorezo cya Koronavirusi ya 2019 (COVID-19) ni indwara nshya, kandi ubumenyi bwacu buzakomeza kwiyongera bitewe n'ubushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'ubumenyi bw'imikorere y'abaganga; bityo, uburyo bwo kumenya indwara n'uburyo bwo kuyivura buzakomeza kuvugururwa.
Muri iyi nyandiko, twashubije ku gitekerezo kimwe cy'ibanze ku buyobozi bwacu kandi dutanga ibipimo bishya byo gusuzuma "abashidikanya" n'"abemejwe" hakurikijwe amabwiriza mashya yo gusuzuma no kuvura COVID-19 (igice cya karindwi) yashyizweho na Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika y'u Bushinwa.
Mu Ukuboza 2019, Coronavirus nshya 2019 (2019-nCoV) yatangiye gukwirakwira, ubu ikaba yitwa byemewe ko ari Coronavirus y'indwara ya 2019 (COVID-2019) kandi iyi virusi ikaba yitwa SARS-CoV-2.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryemeje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo cyugarije isi yose.
