Kuva yatangazwa, yakurikiranwe cyane.
Ibisobanuro Nubwo COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, ubumenyi bwacu buzakomeza kwiyongera bitewe n'ubushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'ubumenyi bw'ibyagiye bikorwa mu buvuzi; bityo, uburyo bwo kuyigenzura no kuyivura buzakomeza kuvugururwa.
Urugero, amabwiriza yo kumenya no kuvura COVID-19 yashyizwe ahagaragara na Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika y'Abashinwa (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), hagati ya 16 Mutarama 2020 na 3 Werurwe 2020, yasohoye imibare irindwi yose hamwe n'imiterere imwe n'imwe yahindutse cyane.
Ubu amabwiriza yacu yaje mu magambo ya Zhou et al. batanze inama yoroheje yo kugenzura ibiba byarabaye mu buvuzi bwabo.
Ibikorwa byabo byatanze ubuhamya bushya ku mabwiriza yacu kandi byerekana ubutwari muri iki cyorezo cyugarije isi.
Turabashimira kandi turabashyigikira mu murimo wabo w'ingenzi.
Ariko, akazi kabo gakeneye kuvugururwa hakurikijwe amabwiriza mashya ajyanye no kumenya no kuvura COVID-19 (Icyiciro cya karindwi cy'igerageza) n'ubushakashatsi bushya.
Nk'uko byemezwa n'Igitabo cya karindwi (ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020), kugira ngo umuntu ukekwaho indwara ashobore kumenya neza niba ari indwara y'icyorezo, agomba guhuza buri kintu cy'ingenzi cy'amateka y'icyorezo n'ibintu bibiri by'ibimenyetso by'ubuvuzi kugira ngo ashobore gukora isuzuma rirambuye, cyangwa se agomba kuba afite ibintu bitatu by'ibimenyetso by'ubuvuzi mu gihe amateka y'icyorezo atari asobanutse neza:
Amateka y'icyorezo: (1) amateka y'urugendo cyangwa gutura mu mujyi wa Wuhan n'uturere tuwurimo, cyangwa mu yindi midugudu aho habayeho amakuru y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu minsi 14 mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira; (2) amateka y'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 (ni ukuvuga ibipimo by'umwimerere by'indwara ya SARS-CoV-2); (3) amateka y'ubwandu bw'abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso cyangwa ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero mu mujyi wa Wuhan n'uturere tuwurimo, cyangwa mu yindi midugudu aho COVID-19 yavuzwe mu minsi 14 mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira; (4) amateka y'ubwandu bw'ubwandu bwemejwe (>= 2 by'abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso cyangwa ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero byamaze ibyumweru 2 mu duce duto, nko mu ngo, mu biro by'ishuri, mu ishuri, n'ahandi.).
Ibimenyetso by'ivuriro ni: (1) ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero n'ibindi; (2) ibimenyetso by'indwara ya COVID-19; (3) imibare y'amaraso y'umweru igaragaza imibare isanzwe, yagabanutse cyangwa yagabanutse y'amaraso mu gihe cy'uburwayi bwa mbere.
Gushyiraho icyemezo cy'uko umuntu yanduye biterwa n'uko hari icyorezo cyangwa ibimenyetso by'ubushakashatsi bw'amaraso: (1) ibipimo by'igihe cy'ubushakashatsi bwa PCR byerekana ko umuntu yanduye SARS-CoV-2; (2) urukurikirane rw'imiterere y'ubwoko bw'umuntu igaragaza ko umuntu ari mu bwoko bwa coronavirus nshya; (3) kuba umuntu yanduye IgM na IgG bya SARS-CoV-2 mu cyiciro cya serum; cyangwa kuba IgG ya SARS-CoV-2 yahindutse kuva ku yindi ikajya ku yindi, cyangwa se kuba umubare w'abantu bakirwaye muri icyo cyiciro cy'uburwayi wiyongera cyane.
Dushobora kubona ko ibipimo bya PCR mu gihe nyacyo by'indwara z'ubuhumekero cyangwa ibipimo by'amaraso byongerewe ku mubare wa kabiri (itariki 18 Mutarama 2020) no ku mubare wa gatatu (itariki 22 Mutarama 2020).
Gushakisha indwara mu bipimo by'amaraso byongerewe mu mubare wa kane (27 Mutarama 2020) no mu mubare wa gatanu (8 Gashyantare 2020); hanyuma hashyirwaho ibihamya bya serolojiya mu mubare wa karindwi.
Izo mpinduka zari zishingiye ku gikorwa gikomeje gukorwa n'abashakashatsi cyo gushaka igikoresho cyo gupima aside ya nucleic cyafashaga mu gupima vuba, hamwe n'ibimenyetso by'umuyoboro w'ubuhumekero harimo n'ibimenyetso by'amaraso, byongereye uburyo bwo kubona ibipimo bitandukanye, kandi byashyigikiye ko haboneka ibimenyetso by'ubwandu bwihariye ku bipimo byemejwe.
Nyamara, hari ibimenyetso byinshi byerekana ko tugomba kwitondera indwara z'ibimenyetso n'iz'uburwayi.
Bityo rero, igishushanyo mbonera cya Zhou et al. kigomba kuvugururwa, kuko bafashe abantu badafite ibimenyetso by'uburwayi nk'abafite "ibyago bike".
Gahunda yo gutanga amanota na yo igomba gusuzumwa mu buvuzi no mu bushakashatsi bw'inyongera.
Ibyo bituma twizera ko hari ibindi bimenyetso bifatika bizatangwa, kandi turasaba abasomyi kugira icyo batubwira.
Kugira ngo tumenye "ibyibazwa" n'"ibyavuzwe", turasaba ko umuntu yakurikirana kandi akurikiza amabwiriza agezweho mu bihugu bye.
