Bangladesh yatangaje abantu batanu bashya bapfuye bazira COVID-19, ari na bwo bwa mbere mu minsi yose.
Ejo, Bangladesh yatangaje abantu bashya batanu bapfuye bishwe na COVID-19 kuri uwo munsi.
Ni umubare munini w'abantu bapfuye umunsi umwe kubera iyi virusi.
Ku munsi w'ejo, Ikigo cya Bangladesh gishinzwe kurwanya no gutoza indwara (IEDCR) cyatangaje umubare w'abanduye, harimo 114 bakomeje gukira, 33 bagumye mu ngo.
Hamaze kuboneka abantu 17 bapfuye.
Mu gusobanura ku rubuga rwa interineti, umuyobozi wa IEDCR, Bwana Mirza Sabrina Flora yavuze ko abapfuye ari abagabo bane n'umugore umwe.
Dr Mirjadar yavuze ko abantu babiri bari bafite hejuru y'imyaka 60, babiri bari hagati y'imyaka 51 na 60 n'undi muntu umwe wari mu kigero cy'imyaka 41-50.
