Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo ku isi hose ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe.
Umuyobozi w'ishami ry'ubuzima rya Bangladesh Anti-Corruption Commission, Jalal Saifor Rahman, wari urwariye mu bitaro bya Quetta, ni umwe mu bapfuye nk'uko byatangajwe n'umukozi w'ishami ry'ubuzima rya Anadolu Agency, ibiro ntaramakuru by'igihugu.
Ku wa gatandatu, mu itangazo ry'amashusho ryashyizwe kuri interineti, Minisitiri w'Umuhanda n'Ibiraro, Ubayidul Qadir, yavuze ko ibikorwa by'urugendo rusange bizakomeza igihe kirekire kurusha uko byari biteganyijwe, kugeza kuri uyu wa Gatandatu.
Gufunga ingendo rusange byatangiye ku ya 26 Werurwe, biteganyijwe ko bizarangira ku wa Gatandatu tariki ya 4 Mata.
