Ubucuruzi muri Ositaraliya bugabanya umubare w'ibikoresho by'isuku mu bucuruzi
Ku wa mbere no ku wa gatandatu nimugoroba, amasoko yo muri Ositaraliya ya Wolverhampton na Coles yagabanyije kugura imyenda y'ubwiherero ku bipfunsi bibiri n'ipfunsi imwe ku gicuruzwa cyose mu maduka yose ku rwego rw'igihugu.
Ku wa mbere, ALDI yashyizeho imipaka y'ipaki imwe.
Ibi bihano byashyizwe ku mbuga nkoranyambaga no ku rubuga rwa Facebook rw'iyi filime.
Byari byatangajwe ko abaguzi baguraga ibintu byinshi kubera gutinya COVID-19 mu gihe abantu bashoboraga kwiherera.
