Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryavuze ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo cyugarije isi yose
Ku wa gatatu, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 - indwara iterwa na virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 - ari icyorezo cyugarije isi yose.
Nubwo ijambo "pandemic" ryerekeza gusa ku kuntu indwara yandura, aho kuvuga uburyo indwara runaka ishobora kuba ikomeye, OMS yagaragaje ko leta zigomba gufata ingamba zikomeye:
Umuyobozi Mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, yavuze ko ibihugu byose bishobora guhindura icyerekezo cy'icyorezo.
Niba ibihugu byigaruriye abaturage babyo, bisobanuye, bikosora, bikatandukanya kandi bikagenzura mu buryo bw'igisubizo.
Dufite impungenge nyinshi kubera ubukana bw'iki cyorezo, ubukana bwacyo ndetse n'uburyo butangaje bwo kucyandura.
Dr Tom Friedin, wahoze ari umuyobozi w'ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara, yavuze ko iki cyorezo "kidashobora kwihanganirwa".
Yavuze ko mu kiganiro cyashyizwe ahagaragara na CNN mu kwezi kwa Gashyantare, "Nta virusi y'ubuhumekero yongeye kugaragara kuva yatangira kugeza aho icyorezo cy'isi cyose gikomeje".
Gabrieleus yavuze ibintu nk'ibyo, agira ati "nta cyorezo cyatewe na coronavirus twigeze tubona".
Yongeyeho ati "kandi ntabwo twigeze tubona icyorezo gishobora kugenzurwa icyarimwe".
Iyi ndwara nshya y'icyorezo ku isi iza nyuma y'icyemezo cya OMS cyo gutangaza mu kwezi kwa mbere ko ari ikibazo cy'ubukungu mpuzamahanga.
