Gukoresha amakuru y'aho umuntu ari kuri telefone ngendanwa na leta ku bw'iyo mpamvu byateje impungenge z'ibanga, aho Amnesty International n'izindi nzego zirenga 100 zatanze ibisobanuro basaba ko hakorwa ingamba zo kugabanya ubwo buryo bwo kugenzura.
Porogaramu nyinshi za terefone zigendanwa zashyizweho cyangwa zashyizweho kugirango zikoreshwe mu buryo bwikora, kandi kugeza tariki 7 Ugushyingo 2020, amatsinda arenga icumi yakoraga ku bikoresho by'ubucuruzi, nko gukoresha Bluetooth kugirango umuntu amenye aho ari hafi ya terefone ze.
Abakoresha bakira ibaruwa iyo bagiranye umubano wa bugufi n'umuntu ufite COVID-19, bakumva ko hari ibitekerezo bibi by'uburyo bwo kwirinda kwandura; urugero, gukaraba amazuru no guhekenya umunwa n'isuku y'umunwa nta cyo bifasha.
Nta rukingo rwa COVID-19 rubaho, nubwo hari imiryango ishobora kuba irimo gukora kugira ngo irushyiremo.
Gukaraba intoki ni ingirakamaro mu kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo.
CDC isaba abantu gukaraba intoki mbere y'igihe bakoresheje amazi n'isabune nibura amasegonda 20, cyane cyane nyuma yo kujya ku bwiherero cyangwa iyo intoki zanduye; mbere yo kurya; na nyuma yo gukaraba, koga cyangwa gukaraba.
Ibyo biterwa n'uko iyo virusi iri hanze y'umubiri w'umuntu, yica ikoreshwa n'isabune, igatuma udusimba tutagira icyo dukora.
CDC yongeraho ko gukoresha umuti wica imyanda ufite nibura 60% by'imyanda mu gihe nta mazi n'isabune biboneka.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima rigira abantu inama yo kwirinda gukora ku maso yabo, ku zuru cyangwa ku kanwa bakoresheje intoki zitahanaguwe.
Imyenda ishobora gukoreshwa mu gihe cy'iminota mike (mu gihe cy'umunota umwe nyuma yo gufatwa n'ikinyabiziga cy'icyuma cy'icyuma cy'icyuma), harimo 62-71% ya isopropanol, 50-100% ya isopropanol, 0.1% ya sodium hydrochlorite, 0.5% ya hydrogène peroxide na 0.2-7.5% ya iyodine-powayodine.
Ibindi biribwa, nka benzalkonium chloride na gluconate ya crohexidine, ntabwo ari byiza.
CDC iratanga inama ko mu gihe hari umuntu ukekwaho cyangwa wemejwe ko afite COVID mu kigo nk'ibiro cyangwa ku kigo cy'ubuvuzi, ahantu hose hakoreshwa ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki nk'ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki, tablette, ecran, tablettes, remote control, na ATM bikoreshwa n'umurwayi, hakwiye gukoreshwa umuti wa virusi.
Imiryango y'ubuzima yasabye ko abantu bambara umwenda cyangwa bakambara umwenda igihe bakoresha cocaine cyangwa pumice, kandi ko uwo mwambaro ugomba guhita usohoka.
Amasahani y'ubuvuzi ni yo ahanini akoreshwa mu bantu bashobora kuba banduye virusi, kuko kwambara agapfukamunwa bishobora kugabanya ingano n'uburebure bw'imirasire y'amaraso mu gihe umuntu arimo ahumeka, avuga cyangwa akankama.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatanze amabwiriza ku gihe n'uburyo bwo gukoresha udupfukamunwa.
Nk'uko Steven Griffin, umuhanga mu by'indwara z'ubwonko muri Kaminuza ya Leeds abivuga, "kwambara agapfukamunwa bishobora kugabanya umubare w'abantu batakaza ibiganza byabo, ari nacyo kintu cy'ibanze cy'ubwandu bw'amaboko adafite isuku".
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatanze inama yo kwambara udupfukamunwa ku bantu bafite ubuzima bwiza mu gihe bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura, urugero nk'abita ku muntu ufite COVID-19, nubwo ryemera ko kwambara udupfukamunwa bishobora gufasha abantu kwirinda gutakaza mu maso.
Ibihugu byinshi byatangiye gushishikariza abaturage gukoresha udupfukamunwa.
Muri Amerika, CDC irasaba abantu kwambara udupfukamunwa tw'impu. Ubushinwa bwasabye abantu bose bafite ubuzima bwiza gukoresha udupfukamunwa tw'impu, cyane cyane mu gihe bari hafi y'abandi (1m (3ft) cyangwa munsi yayo.
Hong Kong irasaba kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe ukoresha imodoka rusange cyangwa mu gihe uri ahantu hakunzwe abantu benshi.
Abayobozi b'ubuzima muri Tayilande bashishikariza abantu gukora udupfukamunwa tw'imyenda mu rugo no kuzajya tuzikaraba buri munsi.
Repubulika ya Czech na Slovakiya zabujije abantu kujya hanze batambaye agapfukamunwa cyangwa udupfukamunwa.
Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Vietnam yasabye abantu bose kwambara agapfukamunwa mu gihe bari mu ruhame kugira ngo bibarinde n'abandi.
Guverinoma ya Otirishiya yategetse ko umuntu wese ugiye mu iduka agomba kwambara agapfukamunwa.
Israel yasabye abaturage bose kumwambika mu maso igihe bari mu ruhame.
Tayiwani, imaze gukora udupfukamunwa miliyoni icumi ku munsi kuva hagati muri Werurwe, yasabye abagenzi bo mu modoka n'amabisi kwambara udupfukamunwa guhera ku itariki ya 1 Mata.
Panama yashyizeho itegeko ryo kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe turi hanze, mu gihe yashyizeho itegeko ryo kwambara udupfukamunwa mu rugo ku bantu badashobora kugura udupfukamunwa.
Amasakaramentu akoreshwa cyane mu Buyapani, Koreya y'Epfo, Malaysia na Singapore.
Kwirinda kwanduzanya (nanone bizwi nka Firiyani) bikubiyemo ibikorwa byo kurwanya indwara bigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara binyuze mu kugabanya ubukana bw'abantu.
Imihanda irimo gutandukana, guhagarika ingendo; ndetse no gufunga amashuri, ibirori, ibibuga by'imikino, amakinamico cyangwa amazu yo guhaha.
Abantu bashobora gukurikiza ingamba zo kwirinda mu buryo bw'imibereho binyuze mu kuguma mu rugo, kugabanya ingendo, kwirinda ahantu higanjemo abantu benshi, gukoresha amagambo yo gusabana atagomba kuvugwa, no kwirinda gutandukana mu buryo bw'umubiri.
Ubu leta nyinshi zisaba cyangwa ziteganya ko abantu bakwirinda guhana imibonano mpuzabitsina mu turere twugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Icyiciro cya mbere cy'amateraniro cyagabanyijwe n'inzego za leta z'Amerika n'inzego z'ubuzima, kiva ku bantu 250 (niba nta cyorezo cya COVID-19 kizwi muri ako karere) kigera ku bantu 50, nyuma kikagera ku bantu 10.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe 2020, Ubudage bwabujije guteranira hamwe abantu barenga babiri. Abantu bakuru bafite ubumuga, bafite indwara ya diyabete, indwara z'umutima, indwara z'ubuhumekero, umuvuduko w'amaraso n'uburwayi bw'ubwirinzi bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara zikomeye, kandi CDC yabasabye kuguma mu rugo mu gihe bishoboka aho ubwandu bwabaye. Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) n'izindi nzego z'ubuzima batangiye guhindura ikoreshwa ry'inshinga "kwitarura abandi" bakayihindura "kwitarura umubiri", kugira ngo basobanure ko intego ari ukugabanya ubwihisho bw'umubiri mu gihe cyo guhura n'abandi, haba mu buryo bw'ikigereranyo cyangwa mu buryo bw'amabanga.
Gukoresha igitekerezo cyo "kwitarura abandi" byasabaga abantu kwifatanya mu bikorwa by'ubutabazi, aho kubashishikariza gukomeza gushyikirana n'abandi binyuze mu mpamvu z'andi mahanga. Hari abategetsi batanze amabwiriza y'ubuzima bw'imyororokere yo kuyikoresha mu gihe cy'icyorezo.
Muri byo harimo inama yo kugirana imibonano mpuzabitsina n'umuntu mubana gusa, ufite virusi cyangwa udafite ibimenyetso bya virusi.
Kwigumira mu rugo ni inama ku bantu bafite COVID-19 cyangwa bakekwaho kuyandura.
Ibigo by'ubuzima byatanze amabwiriza y'ubuvuzi ku bijyanye no kwishyiriraho akarere. Leta nyinshi zategetse cyangwa zasabye ko abaturage bose baba mu turere twugarijwe n'icyorezo bagomba kwiherera.
Amabwiriza akomeye cyane yo kwisanzura ku bantu bari mu byiciro by'abari mu kaga gakomeye.
Ababa baragiranye umubano n'umuntu ufite COVID-19 kandi bakaba baherutse kujya mu gihugu cyangwa akarere kagize ubwandu bukomeye, bagirwa inama yo kwigumira mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 nyuma yo kwandura.
Uburyo bwo kugenzura icyorezo ni ukucyumira cyangwa kucyirinda, no kucyicuza.
Gukumira icyorezo mu gihe cyacyo cya mbere bigamije kumenya no gutandukanya abanduye no gushyiraho ubundi buryo bwo kugenzura indwara n'inkingo zo guhagarika icyorezo kikongera gukwirakwira mu baturage.
Iyo hatagize ikindi gikorwa cyo kugenzura ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo, hashyirwaho ingamba zo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo no kugabanya ingaruka zacyo ku buzima n'abaturage.
Ingamba zo kurwanya no kugabanya ubukana bw'ibicurane zigomba gufatwa icyarimwe.
Gukumira indwara bisaba ingamba nyinshi, ariko kugira ngo umuntu ahindure ikwirakwira ry'indwara ku muntu ku wundi, kimwe mu byo umuntu agomba gukora ni ukugerageza kugabanya ubukana bw'icyorezo binyuze mu gukosora icyorezo.
Ibi bigabanya ibyago byo gukenera serivisi nyinshi kandi bigatuma haboneka igihe kinini cyo gukora inkingo n'imiti.
Ibikorwa bitari ibijyanye n'ubuvuzi bishobora kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo birimo ingamba zo kwirinda umuntu ku giti cye, nko gukaraba intoki, kwambara agapfukamunwa no kwitandukanya; ingamba z'abaturage zigamije kwirinda abantu, nko gufunga amashuri no kwanga guteranira hamwe; uruhare rw'abaturage mu gushishikariza abantu kwemera no kwitabira ibikorwa nk'ibi; hamwe n'ingamba z'ibidukikije, nko kugabanya ubukana bw'amaso. Ibikorwa by'ingenzi byakozwe mu rwego rwo kwirinda icyorezo mu Bushinwa mbere y'uko icyorezo kigaragara, nko gushyiraho ivangura mu mijyi yose no gushyiraho gahunda z'ingendo.
Ibihugu byinshi byashyizeho ingamba zo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi.
Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho ibipimo by'abantu benshi, gushyira abantu mu kato, no kwirinda gutembera kw'abantu banduye.
Singapuru yatanze inkunga y'amafaranga ku bantu banduye bari mu kato, kandi yashyizeho ibihano bikomeye ku batayumvira.
Tayiwani yongereye ingano y'amasashi ikora kandi ishyiraho ibihano ku bantu benshi bagura ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi. Ibigaragara neza mu Bwongereza no muri Amerika bigaragaza ko kugabanya (kugabanya icyorezo aho kugihagarika) no kugabanya (kugabanya icyorezo) ari ingorabahizi.
Gushyiraho politiki nziza yo kugabanya bishobora kugabanya ibyangombwa by'ubuzima ku kigero cya 2/3 n'urupfu ku kigero cya kabiri, ariko bishobora gutuma hapfa abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi amagana kandi bigatuma imibereho y'abantu idakomera.
Gucika ibice bishobora kwemerwa ariko bigomba guhagarikwa kugeza virusi imaze gukwirakwira mu bantu (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rumaze kuboneka, niba ari ubwa mbere), kuko ubwandu buzakomeza igihe ingamba zizaba zarasuzumwe.
Gufata ingamba z'igihe kirekire zo guhagarika icyorezo bizagira ingaruka ku bukungu n'imibereho myiza y'abaturage.
Nta muti wihariye wa COVID-19, ariko hari ibikorwa byo kuwukoresha, harimo no kugerageza imiti ikoreshwa ubu.
Gufata imiti igabanya umubyibuho ukabije, kunywa amazi no kuruhuka bishobora gufasha mu kugabanya ibimenyetso.
Bitewe n'ubukana bw'iyo ndwara, bishobora gukenera ko umuntu afata imiti ya ogisijeni, imitsi yo mu mitsi, ndetse n'ubufasha bwo guhumeka.
Gukoresha ibikoresho by'imikorere bishobora gutuma ingaruka zirushaho kuba mbi.
Ingingo nyinshi zigeze kwemerwa mu kuvura izindi ndwara ziterwa na virusi zigiye gutangira gukorwaho ubushakashatsi ku buryo zakoreshwa mu kuvura COVID-19.
OMS kandi yavuze ko hari "imiti yo mu rwego rwo hejuru" ishobora kugabanya ibimenyetso bya SARX-CoV-19.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryavuze ko kongera ubushobozi n'ubwisanzure bwo kwita ku buzima bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 ari bwo buryo bwo kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo.
ECDC n'ibiro by'akarere by'Umuryango w'Abibumbye byita ku buzima (OMS) byatanze amabwiriza ku bitaro n'ibikorwa by'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze kugira ngo bihindure uburyo mu byiciro bitandukanye, harimo no kugabanya ibikorwa by'ibiro by'ubushakashatsi ku bipimo bya COVID-19, kwanga uburyo bwo kwifashisha igihe cyose bibaye ngombwa, gutandukanya abarwayi bafite COVID-19, no kongera ubushobozi bwo kugenzura cyane hakoreshejwe amahugurwa y'abakozi no kongera umubare w'ibikoresho byo guhumeka no guhumeka.
Hariho ibitekerezo byinshi ku byerekeye aho ikibazo cya mbere (cyitwa indwara ya N°0) cyavuye.
Umuntu wa mbere wamenyekanyeho coronavirus nshya ashobora kuba yongeye kugaragara ku itariki ya 1 Mutarama 2019 mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Mu gihe cy'ukwezi kumwe, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus muri Hubei wariyongereye cyane.
Ibi byose byarebanaga n'isoko rya Huang's seafood wholesale market, aho bagurishaga n'inyamaswa nzima, kandi hari igitekerezo cy'uko virusi ishobora kuba yaturutse ku nyamaswa imwe muri izi; cyangwa, mu yandi magambo, ko yaba ari iy'inyamaswa.
Ku ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan baburiye bagenzi babo ku "virusi ya corona isa na SARS".
Abaganga umunani, barimo Li Wenliang, bari barakanguriwe cyane n'abapolisi kubera ko bakwirakwije poropagande y'ibinyoma, naho undi, Ifen, yarakajwe cyane n'umuyobozi we kubera ko yari yarakanguriye abantu kwirinda akaga.
Nyuma yaho, Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Umurenge wa Wuhan yatanze itangazo ku mugaragaro ku ya 31 Mutarama, kandi iramenyesha Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS).
Icyorezo cy'indwara y'ibicurane by'ubwoko butaramenyekana cyamenyeshejwe abategetsi b'ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa mbere. Mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo, umubare w'abandura wiyongeraga kabiri buri minsi irindwi n'igice.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati ya Mutarama 2020, virusi yageze mu bindi bice by'Ubushinwa, hifashishijwe ibirori byo kwizihiza umwaka mushya w'Ubushinwa n'umujyi wa Wuhan, ahari umuhanda w'indege n'umuhanda wa gari ya moshi.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwatangaje abandi bantu bashya bagera ku 140, barimo babiri mu mujyi wa Beijing n'undi umwe mu mujyi wa Shenzhen.
Nyuma, amakuru yemewe agaragaza ko kugeza ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020, abantu bagera kuri 6174 bagaragaje ibimenyetso. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zabanje Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani, ku isi hose, kugira umubare munini w'abamaze kwandura. Ku ya 9 Mata 2020, ku isi hose, hamaze kuvugwa abantu barenga 1.61 miliyoni, abapfuye barenga 97,000, abamaze gukira barenga 364,000.
Mu bihugu bigera kuri 200 byibasiwe n'iyo ndwara, nibura hari umuntu umwe wayanduye.
Kubera icyorezo cyibasiye Uburayi, ibihugu byinshi byo mu karere ka Schengen byagabanyije ingendo z'abantu ku giti cyabo, ndetse no kugenzura imipaka.
Igisubizo cy'igihugu cyashyizeho ingamba zo kwirinda nko gushyira abantu mu kato (bimwe mu bizwi nka Guma mu Rugo, Guma mu Rugo, cyangwa Guma mu Rugo) no gufunga ingendo. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 300, ni ukuvuga hafi 90% by'abaturage, bari mu rugo, muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, abantu barenga miliyoni 50 bari mu rugo muri Filipine, hafi miliyoni 59 muri Afurika y'Epfo bari mu rugo, na miliyari 1.3 mu Buhinde bari mu rugo.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1.7 ku isi bari mu mimerere runaka yo kuguma mu rugo, ku buryo mu minsi ibiri yakurikiyeho bariyongereye bagera kuri miliyari 2.6 - ni ukuvuga hafi kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wafashwe na COVID-19 ku ya 1 Mutarama 2019 ni Wuhan; raporo imwe idasobanutse neza igaragaza ko umuntu wa mbere wafashwe ku ya 17 Mutarama.
Dr. Zhang Jikshan yabonye ikibazo cy'indwara y'ibicurane by'impyiko bitamenyekanye ku ya 26 Mutarama, bituma ibitaro byamenyesha Wuhan Jiangani ku ya 27 Mutarama.
Igenzura ry'ibanze ry'imiterere y'abarwayi ryabaye ku itariki ya 27 Mutarama 2019 ryagaragaje ko hari virusi ya SARS.
Itangazo rusange ryatanzwe na Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Umurenge wa Wuhan ku wa 31 Mutarama.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryamenyeshejwe kuri iyo tariki.
Mu gihe ibyo bitekerezo byabaga, abapolisi bari baburiye abaganga bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan ko "bakwirakwizaga poropagande" ku cyorezo.
Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima mu Bushinwa yabanje kuvuga ko nta "gihamya gifatika" cy'uko umuntu ashobora kwandura.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, leta y'Ubushinwa yatangije ubukangurambaga bw'intambara, nyuma y'aho ikorwa n'umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka rya gikomunisiti rya China, bwiswe "intambara y'abaturage" yo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi.
Mu byiswe "igihombo gikomeye kurusha ibindi byose mu mateka y'abantu", ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama hatangajwe ko bahagaritse ingendo zijya i Wuhan, zikagera mu migi 15 yo mu mujyi wa Hubei, aho abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 57 bakoreshejwe.
Gukoresha imodoka bwite byari bibujijwe mu mujyi.
Ibirori byo kwizihiza umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa (itariki 25 Mutarama) byasubitswe mu bice byinshi.
Abayobozi batangaje ko imirimo yo kubaka ibitaro by'agateganyo, ibitaro bya Hosinshan, yarangiye mu minsi 10.
Nyuma yaho, hakorewe indi bitaro, i Lichtenstein, kugira ngo haboneke izindi ndwara.
Usibye ibitaro bishya byubatswe, Ubushinwa bwahinduye ibindi bigo 14 by'i Wuhan, birimo amazu y'amateraniro n'ibibuga by'imikino, mu bitaro by'agateganyo. Ku ya 26 Mutarama, leta yafashe izindi ngamba zo guhangana n'icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo gutanga itangazo ry'ubuzima ku ba mukerarugendo no kongera iminsi mikuru y'ibirori bya Spring Festival.
Kaminuza n'amashuri na byo byafunzwe mu gihugu hose.
Akarere ka Hong Kong na Macau kafashe ingamba nyinshi, cyane cyane ku mashuri na za kaminuza.
Imirimo yo gukorera kure yafatiwe mu bice byinshi by'Ubushinwa.
Imipaka ku ngendo zo muri Hubei no hanze yaho yashyizweho.
Itumanaho rusange ryahagaritswe, kandi amazu ndangamurage mu Bushinwa yose yafunzwe by'agateganyo.
Mu mijyi myinshi, hakoreshejwe ingamba zo kwirinda gutembera mu muhanda, aho abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 760 (abarenga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage) bari mu ngendo z'ubwoko bumwe. Nyuma y'uko iki cyorezo cyadutse ku isi hose muri Werurwe, abategetsi b'u Bushinwa bafashe ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda "kwinjiza" virusi mu bindi bihugu.
Urugero, Beijing yashyizeho iminsi 14 yo kwigunga ku banyamahanga bose binjira mu mujyi. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, mu Bushinwa honyine hagezweho umuntu umwe wanduye mu gihugu mu gihe cy'iminsi itanu, muri iki gihe akaba yari umuturage wari uturutse i Guangzhou muri Istanbul.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubushinwa, Li Keqiang yatangaje ko ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo cyandura mu gihugu cyabo ryahagaritswe kandi ko cyakomeje kugenzurwa mu Bushinwa.
Kuri uwo munsi, ingamba zo kugenda zarahumuwe muri Hubei, usibye Wuhan, nyuma y'amezi abiri hashyizweho gahunda yo kuguma mu rugo. Minisiteri y'ububanyi n'amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020 ko kwinjira ku bisa cyangwa gutunga ibyangombwa by'ubwenegihugu bizakomeza kugeza ku ya 28 Werurwe, nta n'ijambo ryihariye rivuga igihe iyi politiki izarangirira.
Abashaka kujya mu Bushinwa bagomba gusaba viza muri ambasade cyangwa muri konsula y'Ubushinwa.
Guverinoma y'u Bushinwa yashishikarije ubucuruzi no gufungura inganda ku ya 30 Werurwe, kandi iha inkunga amashyirahamwe. Inama ya Leta yatangaje umunsi wo kwibuka watangiranye n'umunsi w'agahinda w'iminota itatu ku isaha ya 10:00 ku ya 4 Mata, mu gihe cya Festival ya Qingming, nubwo leta yo hagati yasabye imiryango kwirinda kwivana mu rugo kugira ngo birinde kongera gukwirakwira kwa COVID-19.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020, icyorezo cya COVID-19 muri Koreya y'Epfo cyemejwe ko cyaturutse mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 20 Gashyantare, Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima cyatangaje ko habonetse ubwiyongere bukomeye, ahanini bitewe n'iteraniro ry'abayobozi b'idini rya Daegu ryiswe Shinshyongji Church of Christ.
Abashakashatsi bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan bitaga ku bantu bari mu mujyi wa Daegu, bakekwaho kuba ari bo batumye iki cyorezo cyandura.
Kugeza ku ya 22 Gashyantare, mu bayoboke 9336 ba Kiliziya, 1,261 cyangwa hafi 13% bari bafite ibimenyetso. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko ifite ubukana bwo ku wa 23 Gashyantare 2020.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, muri Koreya hongeye kuboneka abantu barenga 2000 banduye, ku ya 29 Gashyantare habonekaga 3150.
Inzego zose za gisirikare za Koreya ya Ruguru zafungiwe mu kato nyuma y'uko abasirikare batatu bapimwe basanga banduye virusi.
Ibi byagize ingaruka ku byiciro by'indege, bituma n'ibihe by'indege bihinduka. Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho gahunda nini kandi nziza ku isi yo gupima abaturage, gutandukanya abantu bose banduye, gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abanduye.
Uburyo bwo gupima bwagaragaje kwiyamamaza kw'abantu benshi baturutse mu mahanga binyuze kuri porogaramu za telefoni, gupima imodoka ku murwayi wa virusi ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu bagera ku 20,000 buri munsi.
Porogaramu ya Koreya y'Epfo yafashwe nk'igitangaza cyo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo nubwo imijyi yose itari mu kato.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku birego basaba Moon kuburana kubera ko bavugaga ko leta itagize icyo ikora neza ku cyorezo, cyangwa bashima uko yabyitwayemo.
Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Koreya y'Epfo yari ifite ubwandu buke cyane mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bine.
Ku ya 29 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko kuva ku ya 1 Mata ingendo zose z'abanyamahanga zizashyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'ibinyamakuru ku ya 1 Mata, Koreya y'Epfo yakiriye ibyifuzo by'ubufasha mu gupima virusi mu bihugu 121.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Irani yatangaje ko ifite umuntu wa mbere wemejweho SARS-CoV-2 mu gihugu cya Kanum, aho nyuma y'aho ku munsi umwe, abantu babiri bapfuye nk'uko bitangazwa na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi.
Ingamba za mbere zatangajwe na leta harimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'indi mihango y'umuco, imikino, amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu, no gufunga kaminuza, ibigo by'amashuri makuru n'amashuri.
Irani yatanze miriyari eshanu z'amafaranga y'u Rwanda yo kurwanya virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani ku wa 26 Gashyantare 2020 yavuze ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato ahantu hagize icyorezo, ko abantu bonyine bazajya bashyirwa mu kato.
Muri Werurwe hatangajwe gahunda yo kugabanya urujya n'uruza hagati y'imijyi, nubwo urujya n'uruza rwinshi hagati y'imijyi rwatangiye mbere y'umwaka mushya wa Nuruzi.
Kugeza ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020, insengero z'Abashia zo mu kibaya cya Kank zakomeje gufungurirwa abagenzi. Irani yabaye ikigo cy'icyorezo cya virusi mu kwezi kwa Gashyantare nyuma y'u Bushinwa.
Nubwo hari abantu bavuga ko icyorezo cya Iran cyakwirakwijwe, ibihugu birenga icumi byasubiye muri Irani ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, bivuga ko icyorezo gishobora kuba gikomeye kurusha 388 leta ya Irani yari yatangaje icyo gihe.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yafunzwe, aho 23 mu bagize 290 banduye virusi ya Corona ku ya 3 Werurwe.
Ku itariki ya 12 Werurwe, Umuryango uharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu wa Human Rights Watch wasabye abayobozi ba gereza za Irani gufungura by'agateganyo abarwanashyaka b'uburenganzira bwa muntu bafunzwe kubera kwigaragambya mu mahoro, ndetse no gufungura by'agateganyo izindi mfungwa zose zifite agaciro.
Yavuze ko hari ibyago byinshi byo gukwirakwiza virusi mu bigo by'abandura, nk'ibigo by'ubutabazi, aho bitaba ngombwa ko umuntu ahabwa ubuvuzi.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye mu munsi umwe, ari bwo bwa mbere mu gihugu mu munsi umwe kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe, nibura abanyapolitiki 12 cyangwa abahoze ari abanyapolitiki n'abayobozi ba leta muri Irani bishwe n'iki cyorezo.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, Irani yari ifite abantu bashya 50 banduye coronavirus buri saha, n'umuntu umwe upfa buri minota icumi.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umukozi w'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima, muri Irani, umubare w'abanduye ushobora kuba wikubye inshuro eshanu uw'abari bacyemejwe.
Hari kandi igitekerezo cy'uko ibihano bya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika kuri Irani bizatuma igihugu kidashobora guhangana n'icyorezo.
Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku burenganzira bwa muntu yasabye ko ibihano by'ubukungu by'ibihugu byazahajwe n'icyorezo, harimo na Irani, byoroherwa.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, icyorezo cyemejwe mu Butaliyani, ubwo abashyitsi babiri b'Abashinwa bari i Roma bagaragazaga ko banduye SARS-CoV-2.
Imibare y'abanduye ikomeje kwiyongera, bituma leta y'Ubutaliyani ihagarika ingendo zose z'indege zituruka mu Bushinwa, ndetse itangaza ko hari imimerere y'ubukungu bw'ibihe byose.
Nyuma yaho, havumbuwe ikigo cy'abantu banduye COVID-19 badafite aho bahuriye, aho 16 bemejwe mu mujyi wa Lombardy, batangiye ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare. Ku itariki ya 22 Gashyantare, Inama y'Abaminisitiri yasohoye itegeko rishya ryo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo, aho abantu barenga 50,000 bashyizwe mu kato mu mirenge 11 itandukanye yo mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Gusipi Conte yagize ati "Mu bice by'ubutayu, nta kwinjira no gusohoka bizaba byemewe.
Ibikorwa by'akazi n'imikino byategetswe muri utwo turere".Ku ya 4 Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yategetse ko amashuri yose na kaminuza bifungwa kubera ko mu Butaliyani hapfuye abantu 100.
Imikino yose ikomeye, harimo n'imikino ya shampiyona ya Serie A, yari iteganyijwe kuba mu kwezi kwa Mata, ariko ku itariki ya 9 Werurwe, imikino yose yari ihagaritswe by'agateganyo mu gihe cy'ukwezi kumwe.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Gusipi Conte yategetse ko ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi hafi ya byose bihagarara uretse za supermarket n'amavuriro. Ku ya 6 Werurwe, Ikigo cy'Ubuvuzi, Guteza Imbaraga, Gucika no Kubungabunga (SIAARTI) cyatanze inama z'ubuvuzi ku bijyanye na poroteyine z'igenzura zishobora gukoreshwa.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe, Ubutaliyani bwatsinze Ubushinwa mu kugira umubare munini w'abapfuye bazira coronavirus ku isi nyuma yo gutanga amakuru y'abantu 3405 bishwe n'iki cyorezo.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Uburusiya bwohereje indege icyenda z'ingabo zitwaye ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
Kugeza ku ya 5 Mata, mu Butaliyani hari abantu 128,948 bamaze kwandura, 15,887 bapfuye, na 21,815 bakize, abenshi muri bo bakaba bari mu ntara ya Lombardy.
Raporo ya CNN igaragaza ko umubare munini w'abapfuye ushobora kuba waturutse ku mubare munini w'abageze mu za bukuru bari mu Butaliyani, no ku kuba nta bushobozi bwo gupima abantu bose bafite virusi kugeza ubu.
Igisubizo cy'Ubwongereza kuri coronavirus cyatangiye kigaragara nk'igihugu cyugarijwe cyane, kandi kugeza ku ya 18 Werurwe 2020, leta y'Ubwongereza ntiyigeze ishyiraho ingamba zo kwirinda abantu cyangwa gushyira abantu mu kato.
Ibyo byatumye leta inengwa ku kuba itaragize ubushishozi mu gusubiza ibibazo by'abantu. Ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yashyize ahagaragara itangazo rivuga ko abantu bose bagomba gukora ingendo zidakenewe no guhura n'abantu, asaba abantu gukora mu rugo no kwirinda ahantu hatandukanye nko mu mazu y'imyidagaduro, mu birori no mu bitaramo.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, leta yatangaje ko ahantu hose ho gukinira nk'amakipe n'amazu yo kwidagaduriramo hagomba gufungwa vuba na bwangu, kandi yiyemeza gutanga 80% by'umushahara w'abakozi kugeza ku £2500 ku kwezi mu rwego rwo kwirinda ubushomeri mu gihe cy'iki cyorezo. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe yatangaje ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda abantu, kubuza guteranira hamwe abantu barenga babiri no kugabanya ingendo n'ibikorwa byo hanze keretse ari ngombwa.
Uretse n'ingamba za mbere, izi mbogamizi zakurikizwaga n'abapolisi binyuze mu gutora no gutangaza amateraniro.
Ibigo byinshi by'ubucuruzi byategetswe gufungwa, uretse ibigo by'ubucuruzi byitwa ko "bigomba" nka supermarket, farumasi, banki, amaduka acuruza ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi, ibigo by'ibikoresho by'ibikoresho by'amashanyarazi n'amagaraji.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, umuntu wa mbere wanduye COVID-19 mu karere ka Pacific Northwest muri leta ya Washington, yasuwe n'umugabo wari waturutse i Wuhan ku ya 15 Mutarama.
Ku itariki ya 29 Mutarama, hashyizweho itsinda ry'ibiro bishinzwe kurwanya Coronavirus.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubuyobozi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko ari ikibazo cy'ubukungu bw'abaturage, kandi buhagarika ingendo z'abashyitsi baturutse mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kugenzura indwara - ikigo cy'ubuyobozi bw'ubuzima rusange muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika - cyatangaje ko cyateguye ibikoresho byacyo by'ubushakashatsi.
Nubwo Amerika yakoze ibi, yatangiye gutangira gupima buhoro, ku buryo umubare nyawo w'abanduye icyo gihe wari udasobanutse.
Mu kwezi kwa Gashyantare, gupima byari bibangamiye kubera ibikoresho byo gupima imikorere byakozwe na leta, kubura kwemerwa na leta ku bikoresho bitari ibya leta (bikorwa n'amashuri, ibigo by'ubucuruzi n'ibitaro) kugeza mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa Gashyantare, no kugenzura abantu kugira ngo babe bakwiriye gupimwa kugeza mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa Werurwe (bitumye hakenerwa itegeko ry'umuganga).
Kugeza ku ya 27 Gashyantare, Washington Post yatangaje ko muri Amerika hakorewe ibizamini bitarenga 4000.
Kugeza ku ya 13 Werurwe, Atlantic yatangaje ko hasi y'ibipimo 14,000 byakozwe.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, Associated Press yatangaje ko "abantu benshi bafite ibimenyetso n'amabwiriza ya muganga bategereje amasaha cyangwa iminsi yo gupimwa". Nyuma yo gutangaza urupfu rwa mbere muri Amerika muri Washington ku ya 29 Gashyantare, Guverineri J. Insley yatangaje itegeko ry'ubutabazi, igikorwa cyakurikijwe n'ibindi bihugu.
Amashuri yo mu karere ka Seattle yanze kwigisha ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe, kandi mu kwezi kwa gatatu, amashuri yarafunzwe mu gihugu hose. Ku itariki ya 6 Werurwe 2020, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zasabye ko hagira abahanga mu by'indwara z'ibyorezo bo muri kaminuza ya Imperial College i Londres babikoraho ubushakashatsi.
Kuri uwo munsi, Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko ryo gutanga umusanzu uhagije wo kwitegura no gusubiza icyorezo cya Coronavirus, aho yashyizeho miliyari 8.3 z'amadolari muri Fondi ya Leta ihutirwa, agenewe ibigo bya Leta mu rwego rwo gusubiza iki cyorezo.
Amashyirahamwe yashyizeho ingamba zo kugabanya ingendo z'abakozi, kwanga amakoraniro, no gushishikariza abakozi gukora mu rugo.
Imikino n'ibirori by'imikino byarahagaritswe. Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko yahagaritse ingendo mu Burayi bwose, usibye mu Bwongereza, mu gihe cy'iminsi 30, guhera ku ya 13 Werurwe.
Ku munsi wakurikiyeho, yaguye icyemezo cy'uko guhagarika ibyo bihugu byombi ngo kijye mu Bwongereza no muri Ireland.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje ko hari ikibazo cy'ubukungu cy'igihugu, aho yashyize mu bikorwa ibikorwa bya leta mu guhangana n'ikibazo.
Guhera ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, ubucuruzi bwinshi bwafunze cyangwa bugabanya amasaha yabwo yo gukora muri Amerika yose mu rwego rwo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Kugeza ku ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyari kimaze kugaragara mu bihugu byose 50 no mu Ntara ya Columbia. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko umujyi wa New York City wari ufite abantu 10,700 banduye coronavirus, barenga umubare w'abanduye muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 25 Werurwe, Hakeem yavuze ko kwirinda abantu bari kure y'abandi byagaragaye ko ari ingirakamaro, kuko byari byitezwe ko bigabanyuka bikava kuri 2.0 bikagera kuri 4.7 ku munsi.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe, i New York City hari abantu 32,308 bamaze kwemezwa ko banduye, naho 672 bahitanywe na virusi. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ari zo zifite abantu benshi banduye coronavirus kurusha ibindi bihugu byose ku isi, uretse Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani. Kugeza ku ya 8 Mata, muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika hemejwe abantu 400,335 kandi hapfa abantu 12,841.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'ibinyamakuru ku ya 30 Werurwe, Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, Trump, yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera amabwiriza yo kwirinda mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga kugeza ku ya 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, ubwato bw'ibitaro bwa UNSS Comfort bwari bufite ibitanda bigera ku 1000 bwashyize mu mazi y'inyanja i New York.
Ku ya 3 Mata, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zagize umubare munini w'abantu 884 bapfuye bazize Coronavirus mu masaha 24.
Ku ya 3 Mata, muri leta ya New York, abanduye barenze 100,000. White House yanenzwe kubera ko ititaga ku iterabwoba no kugenzura ubutumwa binyuze mu kuyobora abayobozi b'ubuzima n'abahanga mu by'ubushakashatsi kugira ngo basobanure neza amakuru y'ibanze ajyanye na virusi, ndetse no mu biro bya Visi Perezida Mike Pence.
Ubusanzwe, uburyo ubuyobozi bwa Trump bwasubije ikibazo cyabayeho, bwagiye bugabanywamo ibice bitandukanye.
Bamwe mu bayobozi ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika n'abashakashatsi banenze ko Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zishingikiriza ku byo zigurisha mu Bushinwa, urugero nk'ibikoresho by'ibanze by'ubuvuzi.
Isesengura ry'uburyo bwo gutwara abantu mu kirere ryakoreshejwe mu kumenya no guhanura uburyo bwo gukwirakwira, ryasohotse mu kinyamakuru Travel Medicine mu kwezi kwa mbere 2020.
Hashingiwe ku makuru yo mu 2018 yatanzwe n'ikigo cy'indege mpuzamahanga, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo, na Taipei ni byo bihugu bya mbere byabonye abagenzi benshi bivuye i Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne na byo byashyizwe ku rutonde rw'ahandi hakoreshwa ingendo ziturutse i Wuhan.
Bali yagaragajwe ko ari yo ifite ubushobozi buke mu mijyi 20 ifite ubushobozi buke mu bijyanye no kwitegura, mu gihe imijyi yo muri Ositaraliya yagaragajwe ko ifite ubushobozi buke.
Yavuze ko hakiri byinshi byo kumenya kuri COVID-19, kandi ko Australia iri gushyira imbaraga mu gucunga imipaka no gutumanaho mu gisubizo cy'icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe, habaye igitero cya gisasu cy'umuntu muri Ositaraliya.
Kubera ko ingendo rusange z'abantu zikomeje gufungirwa mu mujyi wa Wuhan na Hubei, ibihugu byinshi byateguye gucyura abaturage n'abakozi babyo mu karere, cyane cyane mu buryo bw'indege z'igihugu, ndetse no gusobanurira abategetsi b'Ubushinwa.
Canada, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, Ubufaransa, Argentine, Ubudage na Tayilande ni bimwe mu bihugu bya mbere byatangiye gutegura gahunda yo gusubiza abaturage babyo mu bihugu byabo.
Pakisitani yavuze ko itazasubiza abaturage bayo bose mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 7 Gashyantare, Burezili yasubijeho Abarazili 34 cyangwa abagize imiryango yabo, harimo Abanyapolonye bane, Umunyashinwa umwe, n'Umunyamerika umwe.
