Abaturage ba Brazil bari bagiye i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare kiri hafi ya Brazil.
Kuri uwo munsi, abantu 215 b'Abanyakanaada (abantu 176 bari mu ndege ya mbere, na 39 bari mu ndege ya kabiri yari yaraguzwe na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika) bavuye i Wuhan bagarutse muri Trenton CFB kugira ngo bavurwe mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege ya 185 ya Canada One yageze ku kigo cya gisirikare cya Canada i Trenton.
Guverinoma ya Ositaraliya yajyanye abaturage 277 mu kigo cy'uburinzi cya Christmas Island, cyahawe umwanya wo kuba mu kato, aho bagumye iminsi 14.
New Zealand Air Transport yageze i Auckland ku wa 5/2; abagenzi (bamwe muri bo bari baturutse muri Australia no muri Pasifika) bari mu kato ku kigo cya Hangaru mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku itariki ya 15 Gashyantare, Umuryango w'Abibumbye watangaje ko ugiye kwakira abanyamerika bari mu bwato bwa Diamond Prince.
Ku ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye abagenzi 129 b'Abanyakanaada bari bavuye i Diamond Prince yageze i Trenton, Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, Guverinoma y'Ubuhinde yatangiye gutwara abaturage bayo mu gihugu cya ERA. Ku itariki ya 14/3 indege y'ibinyabiziga ya Afurika y'Epfo yari yakodeshejwe na Guverinoma ya Afurika y'Epfo yazanye abaturage 112 b'Afurika y'Epfo mu gihugu.
Ibizamini by'ubushyuhe byakozwe, kandi abaturage bane bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya coronavirus bashyizwe mu byiciro by'ubugenzuzi bwimbitse kugira ngo bagabanye ibyago.
Abaturage ba Afurika y'Epfo bagaragaye ko banduye ni bo bonyine basubijwe mu gihugu cyabo.
Ibyavuye mu igeragezwa byemeje abaturage bose ba Afurika y'Epfo, harimo abasirikare, abapilote, abakozi ba hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare, ko bakomeje gukora imirimo ya gisirikare. Mu rwego rwo gukemura ibibazo, abantu bose bagumye kugenzurwa kandi bashyirwa mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 muri Ranch Resort.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, Umuryango w'Abibumbye watangiye gushyiraho abasirikare muri Iraq kubera icyorezo.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga wa Sin yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (birimo Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Irani) byatanze imfashanyo kuri Sin.
Bamwe mu banyeshuri ba Sini bo muri kaminuza zo muri Amerika bahuriye hamwe kohereza imfashanyo mu turere twibasiwe na Sini, hamwe n'itsinda rinini ry'abashyize hamwe bo mu karere ka Chicago basangiye raporo bayoboye kohereza udupfukamunwa 50,000 twa N95 mu bitaro byo mu karere ka Hubei ku itariki ya 30/1 .
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko bahaye igihembo cya miliyoni 100 z'amadolari umuntu wese uzashaka umuti wo kurinda "abaturage bo muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Amajyepfo bari mu karere karimo akaga".
Interaction yatangaje ko leta ya Sin yatanze udupfukamunwa 200,000 ku baturage bo muri Filipine ku wa 6 Gashyantare, nyuma y'uko umutegetsi Richard Gordon yohereje udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 mu mujyi wa Wan.
Ku itariki ya 19 Gashyantare, Croix Rouge ya Singapore yatangaje ko izohereza miliyoni 2.26 z'amadolari yo gufasha Sin.
Ubuyapani bwatanze udupfukamunwa miliyoni imwe, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi. Uburusiya bwohereje toni zirenga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu mujyi wa Wan. Malaysia yatangaje ko yatanze imfashanyo ya miliyoni 18 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bya Sin. Ubudage bwohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bya virusi birimo imyenda 10,000 ya hazemat anti-virusi. Umuryango w'Abibumbye wohereje toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Sin, wizeza ko uzabafasha mu bihugu byayanduye. Nyuma y'uko ibipimo by'abanduye muri Sin byibonekeje ko bigiye gukomera, iki gihugu cyatangiye kohereza ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bya virusi mu bindi bihugu byanduye.
