Umucuruzi wa May yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi 1.1 miliyoni, udupfukamunwa 6 miliyoni n'imyenda 60,000 yo kurinda ubuzima i Addis Ababa, Ethiopia, kugira ngo bitangirwe ku rubuga rwa Afurika Yunze Ubumwe.
Nyuma yo kohereza ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi 5,000, ibikoresho by'ubushakashatsi 100,000 n'ibikoresho 5 byo guhumeka, byoherejwe muri Panama.
Twagiye no kohereza ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Canada. Ubuholandi, Esipanye, Turukiya, Jeworujiya na Repubulika ya Czech byatanze ibitekerezo ku bikoresho byo gupima bikoreshwa na Sin.
Urugero, Espagne yashubije ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bya coronavirus 58,000 byakozwe mu cyuma, ku kigero cya 30%.
U Bubiligi bwasubijeho udupfukamunwa 100,000 twari twarakoreshejwe, twitwa ko twakorewe muri Sin, ariko mu by'ukuri twakorewe muri Colombia.
Ku rundi ruhande, inkunga ya Sin yakiriwe neza mu bice bya Amerika y'Epfo na Afurika muri 4/2. Banki y'Isi yatangiye kohereza imfashanyo z'ubutabazi mu bihugu bikennye.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryashimiye cyane Sin ku bw'imihati yashyizeho mu kugenzura no gukumira icyorezo.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ryavuze ku cyorezo cya SARS cyatangiye mu mwaka wa 2002-2004. Leta ya Sin yari yarashinjwe ko yahishe virusi, bituma itangira guhangana n'imihati yo kuyikumira no kuyirwanya, ndetse n'ikibazo cyo muri iki gihe, aho leta y'ibanze "yatangaga amabwiriza yo kwirinda mu biruhuko by'i New York".
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, mu gusubiza icyemezo cya guverinoma y'ibanze cyo guhagarika ingendo mu mujyi wa Wan, uhagarariye OMS Gaudin Galia yavuze ko nubwo "atari itegeko ry'ubuyobozi bw'ishami ry'ubuzima ku isi" ari ikimenyetso gikomeye cyo guhagarika icyorezo mu karere aho virusi yari ikomeye cyane. Yavuze ko ari "ikintu kitazibagirana mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange". Ku ya 30 Mutarama, hakomeje kugaragara ikwirakwira ry'iyo virusi kuva ku muntu kugera ku muntu hanze ya Sin no kwiyongera kw'imibare y'abandura mu bindi bihugu.
Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima, Tedros Adhanom, yavuze ko gutangaza ko habonetse ikibazo cy'ubukungu bw'igihugu, byatewe n' "ubwoba bw'icyorezo ku isi, cyane cyane mu bihugu bikennye n'ibifite ubwisungane mu kwivuza buciriritse".
Mu gusubiza ku itegekonshinga ry'inzibacyuho, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu ihari yo gushyiraho imihati yo kubangamira mu buryo budakwiriye ibikorwa by'ingendo n'ubucuruzi ku isi" kandi ko "isi itemera ko hashyirwaho amategeko agenga ubucuruzi n'ibinyabiziga".
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga gutanga miliyoni 675 z'amadolari yo gufasha ibihugu bikennye, risaba Urukiko rw'Ikirenga gushyigikira ibihugu "bifite uburyo bwo guhangana n'icyorezo, kabone n'iyo byaba biri mu bihe bikomeye".
Tedros yakomeje asobanura ko "itsinda ryacu rizagerwaho n'imihati dushyira hamwe", ndetse n'umuryango mpuzamahanga washishikarije "guha uyu munsi cyangwa ejo hazaza" ku itariki ya 11/02, igihe ubuyobozi bw'ubuzima bw'isi yose bwatangazaga COVID-19 nk'izina ry'icyorezo mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yatangaje ko Jenerali Antonio Gatters ushinzwe ubutasi muri ONU yemeye gutanga "ingabo zose z'umuryango w'abibumbye mu bikorwa".
Umukozi w'itsinda ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ry'ibibazo by'ikibazo yatangijwe nk'ingaruka, atuma habaho ubufatanye bw'umuryango w'abibumbye bwose butuma ubuyobozi bw'ubuzima bw'isi yose "bwibanda ku bisubizo by'ubuzima mu gihe abandi bashyiraho imyanzuro bashobora gutanga ubunararibonye bwabo mu guhuza abaturage, ubukungu no guteza imbere icyorezo".
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, umuyobozi w'itsinda ry'umurimo wo gushyira mu bikorwa amabwiriza y'ubuzima ku isi yakoranye na Sin kugira ngo atange impuguke mpuzamahanga n'amabwiriza y'ubuzima ku isi ya Sin kugira ngo afashe mu igenzura no mu buyobozi bw'igihugu "ku bijyanye n'ubukana n'ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo" atangiza amahugurwa, kandi ahura n'ikigo cy'igihugu cy'ingenzi, no kugenzura ingendo mu karere kugira ngo afate umwanzuro ku "kwiyumvamo kw'ibikorwa by'abantu baba mu bihugu bya kure n'ibindi bihugu, harimo n'imijyi n'imidugudu". Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, World Health Organization yatangaje ko "isi igomba kurushaho kwitegura icyorezo cya coronavirus" ivuga ko mu gihe hakiri kare cyane ko byitwa ko ari icyorezo, ibihugu bigomba "gushyiraho gahunda yo kwitegura".
Mu gusubiza icyorezo cya Iran, WHO yohereje itsinda ry'abantu muri Iran kugira ngo basuzume uko ibintu byifashe. Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, WHO yatangaje ku mugaragaro ko ubwoba bw'icyorezo cya coronavirus ku isi buzamuka buva kuri "cyinshi" bugera kuri "cyinshi cyane", bikaba byemezwa ko ari cyo cyorezo gikomeye kurusha ibindi.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi wa gahunda y'ubutabazi bw'ubutabazi bw'ishami ry'ubuzima ku isi, mu nyandiko yatanze, yaburiye isi ko "hariho ikigeragezo cy'ukuri kuri guverinoma zose zo ku isi: kubyuka.
Virusi ishobora kuba iri mu nzira kandi ugomba kuba witeguye, "kumenya uburyo bukwiriye bwo gusubiza bishobora gufasha isi kwirinda icyorezo cy'icyorezo".
Ryan yavuze ko amakuru ariho ubu atari urwitwazo rwemewe rw'ubuzima rusange rwo gutangaza icyorezo ku isi, avuga ko ari itangazo risobanura ko "twemera ko buri muntu wese ku isi afite ibyago byo kwandura virusi".
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko icyorezo cya Coronavirus ari icyorezo.
Umuyobozi Mukuru yavuze ko WHO "yisanzuye ku kigero gikomeye kandi gikomeye, kandi ko igenda buhoro cyane" ko WHO igomba gusubizaho ibitekerezo by'ingenzi ku gice kitaragaragara cy'icyorezo, harimo gutangaza mu buryo butunguranye icyorezo cy'ubuvuzi rusange no gushyira virusi mu cyiciro cy'icyorezo.
Impungenge z'abaturage zaturutse ku nyandiko y'ubujurire yashyikirijwe Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima, Tedros Adammon, asaba kwegura, yashyizweho umukono n'abantu 733,000 ku wa 6/4.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe, itsinda ry'impuguke mu by'uburenganzira bwa muntu muri Loni ryongeye kugaruka ku ngingo y'uko uburenganzira bw'abantu bose buzakurikizwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Itsinda ry'impuguke ryemeje ko abantu bose bafite ubuzima bwiza kandi ko leta ifite inshingano zo kubikora.
Iri tsinda ryongeye gusubiramo ko kubura umutungo cyangwa ubwishingizi bw'ubuzima bitagomba na rimwe gutangazwa nk'urwitwazo rwo gutandukanya abantu bo mu itsinda runaka.
Impuguke zemeje ko abantu bose bafite uburenganzira bwo guhabwa ubuzima, harimo abantu badafite amikoro make, amoko mato, abageze mu za bukuru, impunzi z'imbere mu gihugu, abatagira aho baba, abakennye, abafunzwe, impunzi z'abakene n'amatsinda atazwi akeneye inkunga ya leta.
Amabwiriza ya leta y'igihugu agaragaza ingaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho myiza y'abaturage mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Ikigo cy'ubufatanye mu by'ubukungu n'iterambere cyatangije urubuga rwo gutanga amakuru arambuye kandi mu gihe gikwiye ku bisubizo bya politiki mu bihugu byo ku isi, hamwe n'ibitekerezo n'inama.
Kuva ku buyobozi bw'igipolisi kugeza ku buyobozi bukomeye bw'ubuzima n'ubukungu ku isi hose kugira ngo hagaragazwe ingaruka z'imihango yo gufunga ingendo no guhagarika ingendo, ikoranabuhanga rigamije gushyiraho polisi y'igihugu ikora, kandi rigamije gufasha ibihugu kwigira ku bindi no koroshya ubufatanye ku isi mu kurwanya coronavirus.
Guverinoma ya Sen yanenzwe n'Umuryango w'Abibumbye n'umunyamabanga w'Ubwongereza muri guverinoma ya Michael Gove n'umuhungu wa Perezida wa Burezili, Eduardo Bolsonaro kubera uburyo bubi yakoresheje icyorezo cyatangiriye muri Sen mu ntara ya Hubei.
Abategetsi b'amashyaka ya Shuwa bo mu ntara za Sin bakomeje kwirengagizwa mu kugerageza gushyiraho akarere ka Sin, mu kugaragaza ko inzego za politiki zititabiriye ibikorwa by'ubwicanyi by'iyo ntara.
Bamwe mu batangabuhamya bavuga ko iki cyemezo cyakozwe mu rwego rwo kurinda umunyamabanga mukuru wa CNDD-FDD, Xinxiang Jinping, inzara y'abaturage muri iki gihe cy'icyorezo cya Coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi ba Sin, urugero nka Zhao Lijian, banze kwemera ko icyorezo cya Coronavirus cyatangiye mu mujyi wa Wan, bashyigikira gahunda ya COVID-19 muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika cyangwa mu Butaliyani.
Ubuyobozi bwa Donald Trump buvuga ko virusi ari "Sini virus" cyangwa "Virus One", buvuga ko abashinzwe kugenzura Sini bakomeje virusi ubu ari icyorezo ku isi. Iyi virusi yanenzwe n'abatangabuhamya benshi bavuga ko ari ivanguramoko kandi ko ari ukwibagirwa ko ubutegetsi bwe bwananiwe gukumira iyi ndwara.
Urubuga rw'amakuru rwa Daily Beast rwabonye ko umwe mu bashinzwe igenamigambi ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ari we ugiye kugirana amasezerano y'ubucuruzi n'ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe umutekano, maze iyo gahunda itangira gusobanurwa mu magambo agira ati "byose ni ku isima".
Tubwirwa ko tugomba kugerageza gukwirakwiza ubutumwa mu buryo ubwo ari bwo bwose, ariko mu nama z'abanyamakuru no mu biganiro byo kuri televiziyo, abantu nka abanyapolitiki, abapolisi b'abanyamahanga na Bloomberg bavuze ko imihati Sin yashyizeho yo gufasha ibihugu byibasiwe na virusi ari uburyo bwo kwamamaza icyorezo cyugarije isi.
Umuyobozi wa Polisi y'Ubumwe bw'Amahanga Joseph Borel, yatanze umuburo ko imiterere ya politiki y'ubutaka bw'icyorezo irimo guhangana n'uburyo bwo gukemura ibibazo n'ubufatanye bwa politiki.
Borel yakomeje avuga ko "Sin ikwirakwiza ubutumwa mu buryo bukomeye cyane ko, bitandukanye n'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, ari umufatanyabikorwa ufite inshingano kandi wizewe".
Sin yanagiye ku muryango w'abibumbye asaba ko habaho guhagarika ibihano kuri Syria, Venezuela na Iran, bavuga ko mbere yo kohereza imfashanyo muri ibyo bihugu byombi.
Impano Jack Ma yatanze y'amamasiki 100,000 yafatiwe muri Cuba n'Urwego rw'Umuryango w'Abibumbye Rushinzwe Ihanwa ry'Ibihano ku itariki ya 3/4.
Umuryango w'Abibumbye kandi washinjwe guhindura intego zo gufasha igihugu kimwe ku giti cyawo.
Amasezerano yo kohereza udupfukamunwa kandi yashyizweho umukono n'ibihugu nka Ubudage, Otirishiya, U Busuwisi, Repubulika ya Czech n'u Butaliyani.
Nubwo byari bimeze bityo ariko, Turukiya yafashe ibikoresho by'ubushyuhe by'ubutaka byari bigenewe Esipanye.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, leta y'Ubutaliyani yanenze inkunga nke y'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi ku barwayi ba Coronavirus mu Butaliyani.
Maurizio Massari, Ambasaderi w'Ubutaliyani muri EU yavuze ko "byari ibisubizo by'abashyigikiye Sin gusa".
Birumvikana ko ibyo bidatanga icyizere cy'uko u Burayi buzabyemera.
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, nyuma y'ikiganiro cya telefoni na Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubutaliyani Giuseppe Conte, Perezida w'Uburusiya Vladimir Putin yateguye ingabo z'Uburusiya zo kohereza abasirikare b'abaganga, imodoka zihariye za microbi, n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
Umunyamakuru w'Umutaliyani witwa La Stampa yashyize ahagaragara ibimenyetso by'uko hari umuntu ukomeye mu bya politiki utaramenyekana, wavuze ko 80% by'imfashanyo z'Uburusiya zitabaye ingirakamaro cyangwa ko zagize akamaro gake ku Butaliyani.
Uyu muyobozi yashinje u Burusiya gukoresha nabi ibibazo (bya politiki n'ububanyi n'amahanga) no gutera ibitero ku mpande zombi.
Perezida wa Lombard, Attilio Fontana na Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga w'Ubutaliyani, Luigi Di Maio, birengagije ibivugwa n'itangazamakuru, maze batangaza ko bishimiye ibyo bakoze.
Uburusiya kandi bwohereje ibicuruzwa by'ubuvuzi muri Amerika.
Umuvugizi wa Kremlin, Dmitry Pesgov, yavuze ko "Putin, mu gihe yoherereza inkunga Umuryango w'Abibumbye, agaragaza ko igihe ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi by'inganda z'Umuryango w'Abibumbye n'ibikoresho byabyo bizaba byuzuye, yiteguye kubishyira mu ishoramari mu gihe bibaye ngombwa".
Imyitozo ya gisirikare ya NATO yo mu mwaka wa 2020 mu Budage, Polonye n'ibihugu bya Baltique, ni imyitozo ikomeye cyane y'intambara kuva mu gihe cy'intambara y'ubutita.
Gahunda y'ingabo za jenerali Kate Hudson yanenze imyitozo ya gisirikare ya 2020 "Muri iki gihe cy'ibibazo by'ubuzima rusange, ibi ntibikunze gushyira ubuzima bw'ingabo za ONU gusa, ndetse n'ibihugu byinshi by'i Burayi, ahubwo n'abaturage b'ibihugu bikora imyitozo ni ahantu habi" Leta ya Irani yahuye n'iki cyorezo, aho abagize Inteko Ishinga Amategeko babiri banduye, n'abantu 15 barimo n'abari barwaye.
Perezida wa Irani Hassan Rouhani yandikiye ibaruwa rusange abayobozi b'isi asaba ubufasha ku wa 14/3/2020, avuga ko igihugu cye gihangayikishijwe n'icyorezo kubera kubura uburyo bwo guhuza isoko mpuzamahanga nk'igitekerezo cyo gufatira ibihano ONU kuri Iran, icyorezo cyatumye bahita bahamagara Umuryango w'Abibumbye kugira ngo bagire uruhare mu guhangana n'ibibazo by'imibereho myiza mu bihugu byateye imbere, birimo ubwisungane mu kwivuza, kwita ku bana bose, umuryango wita ku miryango, n'amafaranga menshi yatanzwe mu rwego rw'ubuzima rusange.
Abasesenguzi mu bya politiki bavuze ko bishobora kugira ingaruka mbi ku isiganwa rya Trump ryo kongera gutorwa mu matora ya perezida ya 2020.
Koreya y'Epfo yanenze "imihati y'uburyarya n'ubushotoranyi" y'u Buyapani. Nyuma y'aho u Buyapani buvuze ko umuntu wese wo muri Koreya y'Epfo agomba kumara ibyumweru bibiri mu kato mu bigo bya leta.
Umuryango wa Koreya y'Epfo waciyemo ibice bibiri ku buryo Sarok Moon Jae-in yitabiriye iki cyorezo.
Abaturage benshi bo muri Koreya y'Epfo batanze ibirego bavuga ko bagomba gufatira Moon urubanza kubera uburyo butari bwiza yakoresheje mu guhangana n'icyorezo cyangwa bagatanga ibisobanuro ku mihati yashyizeho. Icyorezo cyatumye ibihugu byemererwa guca amategeko mu gihe cy'ibihe bidasanzwe.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bavuga ko ibyo byatuma leta zigira ububasha bwinshi.
Muri Hongiriya, Inteko Ishinga Amategeko yemeye ko Minisitiri w'Intebe Viktor Orban ashyiraho amategeko, ko hashyirwaho amategeko agenga amatora, ko hashyirwaho amategeko agenga abatangaza amakuru atari yo ku cyorezo n'uburyo leta yabyitwayemo.
Ikwirakwira rya coronavirus ryatewe n'ingero zitandukanye zirimo kugabanuka k'inkunga. Gukumira ikoreshwa ry'ibikoresho by'intambara mu gihe virusi ikwirakwira ku isi, ibiciro by'ibikoresho, n'imimerere igoye ku nganda n'ibikorwa by'ingendo za gisirikare.
Ikigo cy'Umuryango w'Abibumbye gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti (FDA) cyatangaje ikibazo cy'ibura ry'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bitewe n'ubwiyongere bw'ibyifuzo by'abakiriya n'ibikoresho bipakirwa mu bihe bikomeye.
Ibice byinshi by'igihugu byabonye amafaranga menshi cyane, aho amashami y'ibigo by'ubucuruzi yari acitse, nk'ibiribwa, imyanda, n'amazi, byerekanaga ko ibikoresho byari byaragabanutse.
Ikigo cy'ikoranabuhanga cyatubwiye cyane cyane ku bijyanye n'ibura ry'ibikoresho by'amashanyarazi.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umuyobozi mukuru w'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima, Tedros Adhanom, ibyifuzo by'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku giti cyabo byiyongereyeho 100%.
Ibi byasabye ko ibiciro by'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi byongeraho 20 ku biciro bisanzwe, ndetse no gutinda gutanga ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu gihe cy'amezi ane cyangwa atandatu.
Ibi kandi byateje kugabanuka kw'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi ku isi hose, aho Urwego rw'Ubuzima ku Isi (WHO) rwatangaje ko ibyo bishobora gushyira mu kaga ubuzima bw'abakozi.
Muri Ositaraliya, iki cyorezo cyatumye abacuruzi babona uburyo bushya bwo kugurisha ibicuruzwa byo muri Ositaraliya mu cyaro.
Iki gikorwa cyateje ikibazo cy'ibura ry'amata y'abana mu masuporari, nyuma cyarahagaritswe na leta ya Ositaraliya. Nubwo hari ukwiyongera kw'abanduye COVID-19 mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani no mu ntara ya Wan, kandi hakaba hari ubushake bwinshi bwo kurya neza, ibi bice byombi byarazahajwe n'ikibazo cy'ibura ry'ibiribwa.
Gusaba kwa Sin na Italiya kurwanya ibikorwa byo gukusanya ibiribwa n'amafaranga no gucuruza mu buryo butemewe n'amategeko ibikomoka ku biribwa byafashwe nk'ibyaha, byatsinze ikibazo cy'ibura ry'ibiribwa cyari cyitezwe mu Burayi na Amerika y'Amajyaruguru.
Ibinyampeke byo mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani ntibyigeze bigabanuka cyane, ariko bishobora kuzamuka, nk'uko bivugwa n'abahagarariye inganda.
Ibikoresho by'ibiribwa byabaga byuzuye by'agateganyo, ndetse no mu mujyi wa Wanas, mu gihe abayobozi ba Sin batangazaga ibyokurya by'ingurube kugira ngo bizeze abaturage gutanga ibiribwa.
Hari itegeko nk'iryo mu Butaliyani risaba abahinzi bafungura ibiribwa kugira ngo babishyire mu bubiko mu gihe bibaye ngombwa.
Ibyangijwe ku bukungu bw'isi byumvikanyweho muri Sin; nk'uko byatangajwe n'itangazamakuru ku wa 16 Werurwe, ubukungu bwa Sin bwagize ingaruka zikomeye mu mezi abiri ya mbere ya 2020 kubera ingamba leta yafashe zo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi, ndetse n'ibiciro by'ubucuruzi ku muntu ku giti cye byagabanutseho 20.5%.
Mu gice cy'ingenzi cy'umugabane, ubukungu ni bwo bw'ibanze kandi ni bwo bufite uruhare runini mu bucuruzi. Ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo ribonwa nk'igitera ubwoba cy'ubukungu bw'isi.
Agassi Desmarías wo mu ishami ry'ubukungu ry'ubutasi yavuze ko amasoko azakomeza kuba mu kaga kugeza igihe habonekera ishusho isobanutse y'ibyavuye mu bushakashatsi.
Muri Mutarama 2020, hari abashakashatsi bavuze ko ingaruka mbi z'icyorezo ku bukungu ku isi zishobora kuba zaratumye habaho icyorezo cya SARS cyabaye mu 2002-2004.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'impuguke muri Kaminuza ya Washington muri St. Louis bwavuze ko isi ifite gahunda yo kubitsa miliyari 300 z'amadolari ishobora kumara imyaka ibiri.
Urwego rw'ibihugu by'ibicuruza peteroli (OPEC) rwatangaje ko rwashyize umukono ku cyemezo cy'uko ibiciro bya peteroli byagabanutse cyane bitewe n'uko igiciro cya peteroli cyagabanutse mu gihugu cya Sinayi.
Gufunga amasoko ku isi byatangiye ku wa 24 Mutarama kubera ibimenyetso by'ubwiyongere bw'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 hanze y'igihugu cya Sin.
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare kubera impungenge z'icyorezo cya coronavirus, kubera ko virusi igeze muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika aho NASDAQ-100 yari igiye ku isonga, S&P yari igiye ku isonga mu mirongo itanu, aho Dow Jones yashyize ahagaragara igipimo cy'ubucuruzi bwaguye cyane mu mwaka wa 2008 ku manota 1,191, ari na cyo cyagaragaye ko ari cyo cyagabanutse cyane mu munsi umwe mu gihe cy'ihungabana ry'imari rya 2007-2008.
Byose uko ari bitatu byasoje icyumweru ku kigero kirenga 10%.
