Ikibazo cy'imari cyongeye gutangira kubera ubwoba bwa coronavirus, aho igipimo cy'ibyangijwe cyari hejuru ya 16/3.
Abantu benshi batekereza ko hari icyorezo cy'ubukungu kigiye kubaho.
Umuhanga mu by'ubukungu Mohammed E-Erian yashimiye Banki y'Isi n'ibihugu by'ibanze ku bw'imihati bashyizeho muri iki gihe cy'ihungabana.
Banki nkuru z'igihugu zagize icyo zikora vuba cyane kurusha uko zabyitwayemo mu gihe cy'ihungabana ry'ubukungu rya 2008.
Urugendo ni kimwe mu bintu byazahajwe cyane n'imihango yo guhagarika ingendo, gufunga ahantu hahurira abantu benshi harimo n'aho abantu bajya, ndetse n'inama za leta zo kwirinda ingendo zose ku isi.
Ingaruka zabaye iz'uko ingendo nyinshi z'indege zahagaritswe kubera ko abazikeneye bagabanutse, harimo British Airways, Eastern Airline, na Qantas Airlines, mu gihe akarere ka Flybee Hill kafunzwe.
Ingaruka ku muyoboro w'inganda z'ibikomoka ku nganda zari zigeze kubaho.
Ibibuga by'indege n'ibibuga by'indege byafunzwe
Icyorezo cyibasiye kandi ibirori bya Kinyoni, ndetse n'ingendo nyinshi z'ibihe byose zifitanye isano n'iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya.
Ibiganiro byinshi byahagaritswe n'ubutegetsi bw'ibihugu n'utundi turere, harimo ibirori bya buri mwaka byo kwizihiza umwaka mushya, ndetse n'ibigo by'ubucuruzi by'abikorera byahagaritse ingendo n'ibirori, urugero nka Hong Kong Disneyland na Shanghai Disneyland.
Ibirori byinshi bya Noheli n'urugendo byahagaritswe kubera ko abantu batari bemerewe guteranira hamwe, urugero nk'umugi wa Forbidden City i Beijing n'ibitaramo bya kera.
Mu ntara 24, 31 z'intara ya Sin, utugari n'uturere, leta yongeyeho iminsi mikuru y'umwaka kugeza ku wa 10/2, ndetse abategetsi baburira abacuruzi ko batazongera gufungura kugeza ku wa 10/2.
Izo ntara zari zifite 80% by'abakozi bakora mu gihugu, na 90% by'abahanga.
Hong Kong yazamutse ibisubizo by'icyorezo ku kigero cyo hejuru ndetse itangaza ko hari imikorere y'ubutabazi, ifunga amashuri kugeza muri Werurwe, kandi ikanga kwizihiza umunsi mukuru w'umwaka mushya.
