Ibizamini bya laboratwari ku ndwara ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) ifata umwuka n'ibyiyumvo bijyanye na SARS-CoV-2 birimo ibizamini by'uko virusi ishobora kuboneka n'ibizamini by'uko umuntu ashobora gukora anti-inshura.
Kuhaba kwa virusi mu bipimo byemejwe na RT-PCR ikora ubushakashatsi kuri RNA ya koronavirusi.
Iki cyiciro cy'igerageza ni icy'umwihariko kandi cyateguwe gusa mu bushakashatsi bwa RNA ya virusi ya SARS-CoV-2.
Ibi bikoreshwa mu gushimangira ubwandu bushya kandi bukora.
Ubushakashatsi ku bisigazwa by'amaraso bushobora gukoreshwa mu gupima indwara no kugenzura abaturage.
Ibizamini bya antibody byerekana umubare w'abantu bafite iyi ndwara, harimo abataragaragaza ibimenyetso byinshi cyangwa abataragaragaza ibimenyetso.
Imibare y'indwara n'urupfu rw'abaturage yose bishobora kumenyekana neza binyuze mu gupima.
Nk'uko bigaragazwa n'ibipimo biciriritse, muri Werurwe 2020, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari gifite amakuru yizewe ku ikwirakwira ry'iyo virusi mu baturage bacyo.
Kugeza mu kwezi kwa gatatu, nta gihugu na kimwe cyakoze ibizamini ku baturage barenga 3%, ariko hari ibitekerezo bitandukanye ku buryo ibizamini bikorwa mu bihugu bitandukanye.
Iri tandukaniro rigenda riba igipimo cy'ingaruka z'ubwandu bukomeye, bugomba kuba bufite agaciro gakomeye mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe.
Ikoreshwa ry'imikorere ya polymerase chain reaction (rRT-PCR) isuzuma rishobora gukorwa ku bipimo by'ubuhumekero byafashwe n'ubwoko bwa virusi, harimo gusuzuma mu mazuru no mu mazuru, hamwe n'ibipimo bya LIC.
Ibisubizo bikunze kuboneka mu masaha make cyangwa se iminsi ibiri.
Iperereza rya RT-PCR ryakoreshejwe hamwe n'isuzuma ry'ibicurane ni ryo rigenzurwa rimwe rukumbi mu cyumweru cya mbere cy'uburwayi.
Nyuma yacyo, virusi ishobora guhera mu bwonko ikomeza kwiyongera mu bihaha.
Ku bantu batangiye gusuzumwa mu cyumweru cya kabiri, urugero rw'ibikoresho rushobora gukoreshwa mu gihe cy'ubuvuzi mu buryo bw'ibikoresho byo mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi cyangwa mu buryo bw'imiti.
Imwe mu miti ya mbere ya PCR yatangijwe muri Kaminuza ya Charité i Berlin muri Mutarama 2020 ikoresha imikorere ya polymeric chain reaction (rRT-PCR).
Ubwongereza bwakoze igerageza ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama 2020. Ikigo cyo muri Koreya y'Epfo cyitwa Cogenebiotic cyashyizeho uburyo bushya bwo kuvura, PCR ikoreshwa mu gupima SARS-CoV-2 (kugenzura virusi ya corona mu buryo bwimbitse) ku itariki ya 28 Mutarama 2020.
Ikizamini cyashakishije ubwoko bwa "E" bw'ikinyabutabire cyakwirakwijwe muri virusi ya coronavirus, n'ubwoko bwa RdRp bwihariye bwa SARS-CoV-2. Mu mwaka wa 2019, BGI Group ni umwe mu bihugu bya mbere byabonye ibikoresho by'ubutabazi by'ibanze byavuye muri Minisiteri y'Ubuzima bw'Ibise, PCR ishingiye ku bikoresho byo gupima SARS-CoV-2, muri Amerika, kandi ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) cyashyize ahagaragara icyiciro gishya cya 2019 coronavirus test (RT-PCR) cy'ibinyabutabire mu bigo nderabuzima binyuze mu bikoresho mpuzamahanga by'ubushakashatsi.
Kimwe mu bipimo by'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima byakozwe ku buryo bw'ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga cyatumye haboneka ibisubizo by'ibanze bitemewe kubera ko hakoreshejwe ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga bidafite aho bigeze n'ibirahuri byo gupima mu kigo cy'ubuvuzi cya CDC cyo muri Atlanta; ibyo byatumye haboneka ibipimo biri munsi y'100 ku munsi muri Gashyantare 2020.
Ibipimo by'ibikoresho bibiri bitandukanye ntibyari byemejwe neza ku ya 28/2/2020. Kugeza icyo gihe, byatangajwe ko ibigo by'ikoranabuhanga byo mu gihugu n'ibya leta byemerewe gukora ibizamini.
Ibizamini byemewe n'ikigo gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti cya leta byatangiye gukorwa mu buryo bwihutirwa. Laboratwari za ONU zatangiye gukora ibizamini mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020.
Ku itariki ya 5/3/2020, LabCorp yatangaje ko ibipimo bya COVID-19 byashyizwe ku isoko ku rwego rw'igihugu bishingiye kuri RT-PCR
Ikigo gishinzwe gusuzuma indwara cyasohoye kandi icyemezo cy'igihugu cyo gusuzuma COVID-19 ku itariki ya 9/3/2020.
Nta mibare yemewe, kandi isubirwamo ry'ibipimo n'ubugenzuzi bigomba gukorwa hakurikijwe ibisabwa na CDC.
Mu Burusiya, ibizamini bya COVID-19 byatangijwe kandi byakozwe n'ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi ku mikorobe na virusi (VECTOR).
