Ku ya 19/3/2020, FDA yemeje EUA Laboratories ya Abbott ku buryo bwemewe kugira ngo ikore ibizamini kuri sisitemu ya Abbott ya metero 2000. FDA yabanje guha ububasha bwo kwemerera ibintu bitandukanye nka Hologic, LabCorp na Sermo Fisher Scientific.
Ku ya 21/3/2020, Seyfed na we yahawe uruhushya na FDA rwo gukora ikizamini cyamusabaga iminota 45.
FDA yemeye isuzuma rikoresha ikoranabuhanga rya acide nucléique mu cyimbo cya PCR.
Kubera ko bidasaba ko habaho guhindura ubushyuhe mu buryo butandukanye, ubu buryo bushobora gutanga ibisubizo by'ibizamini byemeza mu minota 5 gusa, n'ibisubizo by'ibizamini byemeza mu minota 13.
Ubu muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika hari ibikoresho bigera ku 18,000. Abbott ateganya ko bizagera ku bipimo bigera ku 50,000 ku munsi. Ikigeragezo gikoresha antibodies n'ibisasu by'ubwoko butandukanye by'uruhu (N protein) rwa coronavirus iherutse kwandura kirimo gukorwa muri Tayiwani, aho hari icyizere ko kizatanga ibisubizo mu minota 15 kugeza kuri 20 nk'uko byagenze mu gupima ibicurane byihuse.
Isuzuma ry'ibitabo ryo muri Werurwe 2020 ryagaragaje ko "ibishushanyo by'ibinyabiziga by'igituza bifite uruhare ruto mu kugaragaza indwara mu byiciro bya mbere. Mu gihe byibonekeye kuri CT (ibishushanyo by'ibinyabiziga bibarurwa) bishobora kuba mbere y'ibimenyetso bya mbere".
Imyitozo isanzwe kuri CT ikubiyemo ibikoresho by'amashusho by'ibyiciro byinshi, imashini y'imashini y'imashini, imashini idatunganye n'ibisate by'inyuma.
Ubwiyongere bw'ibinyabiziga, uburwayi bw'ibinyabiziga n'ubundi budafite ubukana, bifatwa nk'indwara y'ubwiyongere.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko PCR ari yo igaragaza indwara z'ibicurane, ariko ko CT ari yo igaragaza neza indwara z'ibicurane, ndetse ko ari yo igaragaza neza indwara z'ibicurane.
Muri Werurwe 2020, Ishuri ry'Ubuvuzi rya Radiation Society muri Amerika ryatangaje ko "CP ikwiye kudakoreshwa mu gupima no gupima virusi ya COVID-19". Muri Werurwe 2020, CDC yatangaje ko PCR yemewe mu gupima ku ncuro ya mbere.
Igice cy'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri ku cyorezo ni ugukora antibodies zirimo IgM na IgG.
Ibi bishobora gukoreshwa mu gupima abantu mu minsi 7 y'ubwandu cyangwa nyuma yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso by'ibanze mu gupima ubwirinzi bw'umubiri no gupima indwara mu gihe cy'uburwayi. Ibizamini bishobora gukorwa mu bigo bya laboratwari (CLT) cyangwa mu gupima ku mwanya w'ububiko (PoCT).
Ibipimo by'ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga mu bigo by'ubuvuzi bizaba bihagije kugira ngo bikore ibi bizamini, ariko kuboneka bizaterwa n'ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga by'ikoranabuhanga.
