Nk'uko OSHA ibivuga, abantu bafite ibyago by'akazi harimo abafite umubano wa hafi cyangwa wa hafi n'abantu bafite uburebure bwa metero esheshatu (1.8m) batanduye cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura SARS-CoV-2 bitewe no kwandura mu bantu benshi cyangwa bitewe n'uko umuntu yagiye mu mahanga mu karere ka COVID-19.
Izi zikubiyemo abakozi bahuza ahantu rusange nk'amashuri, ahantu ho gukoreramo inganda cyangwa ahantu ho guhaha no kugurisha. Inguzanyo yo kugenzura ibi n'amatsinda y'ibyago bikomeye harimo gushyiraho filtri za kirere zigezweho, kongera umubare w'ibikoresho bihumanya ikirere, gushyiraho inzitizi z'ubuvuzi nka protective ya plastiki yo mu gikoni no gushyiraho serivisi yo kugeza ku bakiriya.
Abakozi bo muri iri tsinda ry'abanduye ntibakunze gusabwa gukoresha imashini zifasha guhumeka.
Iyo umuntu arwaye ku kibuga cy'indege, hakorwa ingamba zifatika zo kurinda abakozi n'abagenzi, harimo gutandukanya umurwayi n'abandi bantu ku burebure bwa metero 6, no gushyiraho itsinda ry'abantu bazajya bareba umurwayi, guha umurwayi agapfukamunwa cyangwa gusaba umurwayi ko yakoresha umuti wo kumurinda mu kanwa igihe anuka cyangwa asoma.
Abakozi b'itsinda bagomba kwambara amaguru y'ibanga igihe bahanganye n'umunyururu urwaye cyangwa se igihe bakoresheje amazi yo mu mubiri cyangwa imyanda, kandi bagakoresha ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bw'umuntu mu gihe uwo munyururu arwaye cyangwa afite ikibazo cyo guhumeka.
Ibikoresho byo kurinda intoki n'ibikoresho bigomba gutangwa mu mifuka ya plastiki, kandi imyanda igomba gukorerwa isuku no gukingirwa. Ku masoko y'ibikoresho by'ibanze, harimo kugurisha no gutwara abantu, kugenzura ibyangiritse birimo gutinda urugendo mu gihe umuntu arwaye cyangwa kwigumira mu kato no kumenyesha mu buryo butaziguye ikigo nderabuzima cy'ubwato mu gihe umuntu yaba yaranduye cyangwa afite ibindi bimenyetso ku bwato.
Ubusanzwe, umuntu utagomba kujya mu kato agomba kuba afite imiti. Amashuri, urwego rw'abana n'Ikigo cy'Ubuvuzi cy'Igihugu cy'Icyorezo cy'Amateka n'Icyorezo cy'Indwara z'Imyuka (CDC) byatangaje ko hari igihe gito cyo gufunga ku buryo umuntu wafashwe n'icyorezo ashobora kuba ari mu cyumba cy'ishuri, mu gihe hari icyorezo cy'icyorezo cy'indwara.
Iyo nta gikorwa cyakozwe cyo kugabanya ubwiyongere bw'abantu, uburyo bwo gutandukanya abantu bushobora gushyirwa mu bikorwa nko kwanga ingendo, amateraniro n'ibindi biganiro bikomeye nk'amasomo y'ubuvuzi cyangwa amateraniro y'idini cyangwa gusangira mu kabari, kongera igihe cyo gufungura hagati y'ameza no gutegura ingendo n'ikiruhuko cy'abanyeshuri, no kugabanya ingendo zidakenewe no gukoresha ahantu ho kwa muganga ku bana bafite ibimenyetso bya grippe.
Iyo hari icyorezo gikomeye mu baturage, nubwo hari uburyo bwo gutandukanya abantu, ikiruhuko cy'amashuri gishobora gutekerezwa. Ku mategeko y'ibiro by'ubuyobozi agenga ibikorwa by'imikorere ya buri munsi, ibyago by'ubuzima by'ibanze bifatwa nk'ibidashoboka na CDC.
