Impyiko ni zo zifatwa cyane na COVID-19 kuko virusi yinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'amaraso binyuze mu cyitwa angiotensin-likelike enzyme 2 (ACE2), ari na cyo cyitwa ubwoko bwa 2 bw'imikorere y'imikorere y'amaraso.
Iyi virusi ikoresha uruhu rwihariye rwa virusi ya diabete bita "peplomer" kugira ngo ikoreho ACE2 kandi ikoreho mu cyumba cy'umunyamubiri.
Indwara y'umutima ikomeye yagaragaye mu 12% by'abarwayi bari mu bitaro by'i Wan, Sin, kandi akenshi yagaragaye mu barwayi bakomeye.
Indwara ya Nerve Heart syndrome ifite ibimenyetso byinshi, bigatuma habaho guhungabana kw'imikorere y'umubiri n'uburwayi bw'ubwirinzi, ariko gusenyuka kw'imitsi y'umutima bishobora kuba bifitanye isano na ACE2 mu mutima.
ACE2 ni ingirabuzimafatizo z'umutima zigaragara cyane mu buryo bw'umutima.
Ibipimo byo hejuru by'amaraso (31%) n'amaraso (25%) byibonekeye mu barwayi ba ICU banduye COVID-19 kandi bishobora kuba bifitanye isano no kutagira amahirwe yo gukira.
Nubwo SARS-CoV-2 ifite ubushobozi bwo kugaragaza ACE2 mu nsoro z'ubuhumekero z'umubiri, abarwayi bafite COVID-19 ikomeye bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara y'ubuhumekero.
