Ni indwara n'agakoko gatera indwara, bita coronavirus.
Mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya mbere cyabaye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, virusi n'indwara byavuzwe muri rusange ko ari "Coronavirus" na "Wuhan Coronavirus".
Muri Mutarama 2020, OMS yasabye ko 2019-nCov na 2019-corona virusi z'icyorezo ari amazina abiri y'igihe cy'indwara na virusi mu bijyanye n'amabwiriza yo mu 2015 yo kwirinda gukoresha ahantu mu kuvura indwara no mu kuvura indwara.
Amazina yemewe ya COVID-19 na SARS-CoV-2 yasohotse ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020.
