Kuva COVID-19 yatangira, hari ibinyoma, ibitekerezo n'ibinyoma byibanda ku nkomoko, igipimo, uburyo bwo kwirinda, imiti cyangwa ibindi byatuma indwara ikwirakwira ku buryo bwihuse kuri interineti.
