Nta miti cyangwa imiti yemewe yo kuvura iyi ndwara.
Ubushakashatsi mpuzamahanga ku miti na imiti ya COVID-19 bukorwa n'inzego za leta, amatsinda y'abahanga n'abashakashatsi mu by'inganda.
Mu kwezi kwa Mata, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangiye gukora igerageza ry'ibanze rya 'SOLIDARITY Trial' kugira ngo rigaragaze ko imiti y'imiti ine ya virusi itera SIDA ifite ubushobozi buhambaye.
Nta misemburo iboneka, ariko impande zitandukanye zikora cyane mu guhanga imisemburo.
Ibikorwa bya mbere kuri SAES-CoV byari bifite akamaro kuko SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 byombi bikoresha ACE2 mu kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'umuntu.
Batatu muri bo bakurikiranwe n'abapolisi ba Kutan.
Icya mbere, ubushakashatsi bugamije gukora umuti wa virusi.
Gukoresha virusi zidakira cyangwa zidakira mu rwego rwo kwihutisha uburyo umubiri w'umuntu ukora mu gihe cy'ubwandu bushya bwa COVID-19.
Uburyo bwa kabiri, ni uko hakorwa imiti ifasha umubiri kwirinda ibice by'ubwandu.
Ku byerekeranye na SARS-CoV-2, ubu bushakashatsi bwibanda ku poroteyine ya S-spike ifasha virusi kwinjira mu gice cya ACE2.
Uburyo bwa gatatu, ni ugufata imiterere ya nucleic acid (imiterere ya ADN cyangwa RNA, uburyo bushya bwo gukora kuriya).
Kugerageza imiti muri buri bumwe muri ubu buryo bisaba ko ikorwaho igerageza ry'umutekano n'ibya ngombwa. Ku itariki ya 16 Werurwe 2020 hatangiye igerageza rya mbere ry'imiti ku bantu bane b'abakorerabushake bo mu mujyi wa Seattle.
Uru rukingo rugizwe n'imiterere y'imiterere y'umubiri udafite ubukana, ituruka kuri virusi iteza iyi ndwara.Kugira ngo hakorwe uburyo bwo kongera ubushobozi bw'umubiri, byavuzwe ko ari cyo kibazo gikomeye cyo guhangana n'ubwiyongere bw'imiterere ya 2-SARS-CoV, ariko ibyo biracyari impaka.
Muri Mata 2020, habaye ibizamini by'ubuvuzi birenga 300.
Hari ibizamini birindwi byagenzuwe kandi byemejwe ko bivura indwara ya malariya, harimo n'ibindi bine by'ubushakashatsi ku cyitwa hydrochloricillin cyangwa chloricillin.
Byari byitezwe ko ubushakashatsi bwinshi mu Bushinwa buzaba bushingiye ku miti ya virusi, hamwe n'imihati icyenda yo mu cyiciro cya gatatu yo kugerageza umuti wa Redivivir mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe, kugeza mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa kane.
Iterambere ry'ikigo cy'ubuvuzi cy'ibyigenge cy'imiterere ya COVID-19 n'imiti y'ikirenga byatangiye mu kwezi kwa Mata 2020. Hari imiti imwe na imwe ya virusi irimo gusuzumwa mu kuvura COVID-19, harimo Remdicivir na Hydrochloruquin, Lopinvir/Ritonavir na Lopinavir/Ritonavir, byashyizwe hamwe mu gutangiza beta-blockers.
Hari ibimenyetso by'agateganyo byerekana ko umuti wa Remdesivir ufite ingaruka, nko muri Gicurasi 2020.
Umubare w'abarwayi bavurwa indwara z'ihungabana bakoresheje Remdesivir, wagiye wiyongera.
Icyiciro cya gatatu cy'igerageza ry'ubuzima cyakozwe muri Amerika, Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani. Ihororokwini yari yarigeze gukoreshwa mu kuvura malariya, yasuzumwe mu Bushinwa mu kwa kabiri 2020 n'ibisubizo by'ibanze.
Icyakora, hari abafata umwanzuro wo gusuzuma icyo gitabo.
Ubutegetsi bwa Koreya n'ikigo cy'ubuzima cyavuze ko gukoresha chlorokwin ari byiza.
Nyamara, Ikigo cya Wuhan gishinzwe ubushakashatsi ku mikorobe, mu gihe gitanga inama y'ifunguro rimwe ku munsi ku kigero cya 1 gram, kivuga ko kureka kurya inshuro ebyiri ku munsi ari ibintu bishobora guteza akaga.
Ku ya 28 Gicurasi 2020, FDA yatangaje ko ikoresha mu buryo bw'impanuka za hydrochloricotine na chloricotine mu gufata ibyemezo by'ubuvuzi ku bantu bafite COVID-19.
Amakuru ya mbere agaragaza ko ifunguro ryinshi rya ribavirin ari ngombwa mu kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 mu buryo bwa vitro.
Nitazoxanide yagaragajwe ko ari umuti ushobora gukoreshwa mu gutunganya SARS-CoV-2 mu gihe cy'inzara. Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko poroteyine ya mbere y'ibinyamubiri itangwa na TMPRSS2 ari yo ituma SARS-CoV-2 ikora ikorana na ACE2.
Ibipimo bya chloroquine na hydroxychloroquine bifatanyije na antibacterial cyangwa antibacterial bifite imipaka myinshi ituma umuryango w'ubuvuzi udashobora kwemeza ko imiti nk'iyi ikoreshwa nta bushakashatsi bwimbitse bwakozwe. Oseltamivir ntabwo ihagarika SARS-CoV-2 kandi nta ruhare ifite mu kuvura COVID-19.
Umwikubo w'ibikomoka kuri sitokayine ushobora kuba ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi mu cyiciro cya nyuma cya COVID-19 ikomeye.
Hari ibimenyetso byerekana ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora kugira imyitwarire yo kurwanya cytokine. Tocilizumab yashyizwe ku rutonde rw'imiti yavuye muri ICRC nyuma y'ubushakashatsi buciriritse.
Ni icyiciro cy'igerageza ry'ibizamini bibiri by'amahanga bitemewe mu Butaliyani, aho abantu babiri bagaragaye ko banduye indwara ikomeye.
Iyo uhujwe n'ibipimo by'amaraso bikoreshwa mu gupima indwara z'ubwandu bwa cytokine, bishobora gutuma umuntu apfa mu bantu bamwe na bamwe bayanduye.
Cytotoxin-receptor antagonist -6 yemewe na FDA hashingiwe ku bushakashatsi bwa mbere bwo kuvura ibimenyetso by'indwara ya steroid.
Kugeza ubu, nta bimenyetso bifatika cyangwa by'ubuziranenge bigaragaza ko tocilizumab ari umuti w'indwara ya CRS.
